#: reader.lua:194
msgid ""
"Documents will be rendered in color on this device.\n"
"If your device is grayscale, you can disable color rendering in the screen "
"sub-menu for reduced memory usage."
msgstr ""
"Déanfar doiciméid a rindreáil i ndath ar an ngléas seo.\n"
"Más liathscála atá i do ghléas, is féidir leat rindreáil dathanna a "
"dhíchumasú i bhfo-roghchlár an scáileáin chun úsáid chuimhne a laghdú."

#: reader.lua:202
msgid ""
"Color rendering is mistakenly enabled on your grayscale device.\n"
"This will subtly break some features, and adversely affect performance."
msgstr ""
"Tá rindreáil datha cumasaithe trí dhearmad ar do ghléas liathscála.\n"
"Cuirfidh sé seo isteach go héadrom ar roinnt gnéithe, agus cuirfidh sé "
"isteach go diúltach ar fheidhmíocht."

