"The font list menu can show fonts sorted by name or by most recently "
"selected.\n"
"New fonts discovered at KOReader startup will be shown first.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to clear the history of selected fonts?"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leis an roghchlár liosta clónna atá sórtáilte de réir ainm nó de "
"réir na gclónna is déanaí a roghnaíodh a thaispeáint.\n"
"Taispeánfar clónna nua a aimsítear ag am tosaithe KOReader ar dtús.\n"
"\n"
"Ar mhaith leat stair na gclónna roghnaithe a ghlanadh?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerfont.lua:726
msgid "Use additional fallback fonts"
msgstr "Úsáid clónna breise cúltaca"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerfont.lua:735
msgid ""
"Enable additional fallback fonts, for the most complete script and language "
"coverage.\n"
"These fonts will be used in this order:\n"
"\n"
"%1\n"
"\n"
"You can set a preferred fallback font with a long-press on a font name, and "
"it will be used before these.\n"
"If that font happens to be part of this list already, it will be used first."
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh clónna breise cúltaca, le haghaidh an chlúdaigh scripte agus "
"teanga is iomláine.\n"
"Úsáidfear na clónna seo san ord seo:\n"
"\n"
"%1\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat cló cúltaca is fearr leat a shocrú le brú fada ar ainm cló, "
"agus úsáidfear é roimh na cinn seo.\n"
"Más rud é go bhfuil an cló sin mar chuid den liosta seo cheana féin, "
"úsáidfear é ar dtús."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerfont.lua:746
msgid "Adjust fallback font sizes"
msgstr "Coigeartaigh méideanna clónna cúltaca"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerfont.lua:755
msgid ""
"Adjust the size of each fallback font so they all get the same x-height, and "
"lowercase characters picked in them look similarly sized as those from the "
"default font.\n"
"This may help with Greek words among Latin text (as Latin fonts often do not "
"have all the Greek characters), but may make Chinese or Indic characters "
"smaller when picked from fallback fonts."
msgstr ""
"Coigeartaigh méid gach cló chúltaca ionas go bhfaighidh siad uile an airde-x "
"chéanna, agus go mbeidh cuma chomhchosúil ar na carachtair bheaga a "
"roghnaítear iontu agus atá ar na cinn ón gcló réamhshocraithe.\n"
"D’fhéadfadh sé seo cabhrú le focail Ghréagacha i measc téacs Laidine (ós rud "
"é nach mbíonn na carachtair Ghréagacha go léir i gclónna Laidine go minic), "
