#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerfooter.lua:1521
msgid ""
"This option will hide inactive items from appearing on the status bar. For "
"example, if the frontlight is 'off' (i.e 0 brightness), no symbols or values "
"will be displayed until the brightness is set to a value >= 1."
msgstr ""
"Cuirfidh an rogha seo míreanna neamhghníomhacha i bhfolach ó bheith le "
"feiceáil ar an mbarra stádais. Mar shampla, má tá an solas tosaigh 'múchta' "
"(i.e. 0 gile), ní thaispeánfar aon siombailí ná luachanna go dtí go socrófar "
"an gile go luach >= 1."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerfooter.lua:1534
msgid "Include current page in pages left"
msgstr "Cuir an leathanach reatha san áireamh sna leathanaigh ar chlé"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerfooter.lua:1535
msgid ""
"By default, KOReader does not include the current page when calculating "
"pages left. For example, in a book or chapter with n pages the 'pages left' "
"item will range from 'n−1' to 0 (last page).\n"
"With this feature enabled, the current page is factored in, resulting in the "
"count going from n to 1 instead."
msgstr ""
"De réir réamhshocraithe, ní chuireann KOReader an leathanach reatha san "
"áireamh agus leathanaigh atá fágtha á ríomh. Mar shampla, i leabhar nó i "
"gcaibidil le n leathanach, beidh an mhír 'leathanaigh atá fágtha' idir 'n−1' "
"agus 0 (an leathanach deireanach).\n"
"Nuair a bhíonn an ghné seo cumasaithe, cuirtear an leathanach reatha san "
"áireamh, rud a fhágann go n-athraíonn an comhaireamh ó n go 1 ina ionad."

