#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:157
msgid "About custom table of contents"
msgstr "Maidir le clár ábhair saincheaptha"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:160
msgid ""
"If the book has no table of contents or you would like to substitute it with "
"your own, you can create a custom TOC. The original TOC (if available) will "
"not be altered.\n"
"\n"
"You can create, edit and remove chapters:\n"
"- in Page browser, by long-pressing on a thumbnail;\n"
"- on a book page, by selecting some text to be used as the chapter title.\n"
"(Once you're done building it and don't want to see the buttons anymore, you "
"can disable Edit mode.)\n"
"\n"
"This custom table of contents is currently limited to a single level and "
"can't have sub-chapters."
msgstr ""
"Mura bhfuil clár ábhair sa leabhar nó más mian leat é a chur ina áit le do "
"chuid féin, is féidir leat TOC saincheaptha a chruthú. Ní athrófar an TOC "
"bunaidh (más ann dó).\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat caibidlí a chruthú, a chur in eagar agus a bhaint:\n"
"- sa bhrabhsálaí leathanaigh, trí bhrú fada ar mhionsamhail;\n"
"- ar leathanach leabhair, trí théacs a roghnú le húsáid mar theideal na "
"caibidle.\n"
"(Nuair a bheidh tú críochnaithe leis an gcaibidil agus mura mian leat na "
"cnaipí a fheiceáil a thuilleadh, is féidir leat an mód Eagarthóireachta a "
"dhíchumasú.)\n"
"\n"
"Tá an clár ábhair saincheaptha seo teoranta do leibhéal amháin faoi láthair "
"agus ní féidir fo-chaibidlí a bheith ann."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:174
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:235
msgid "Edit mode"
msgstr "Mód eagarthóireachta"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:192
msgid "Clear custom table of contents"
msgstr "Glan an clár ábhair saincheaptha"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:198
msgid "Are you sure you want to clear your custom table of contents?"
msgstr ""
"An bhfuil tú cinnte gur mian leat do chlár ábhair saincheaptha a ghlanadh?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:214
msgid "About custom hidden flows"
msgstr "Maidir le sreafaí folaithe saincheaptha"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:217
msgid ""
"Custom hidden flows can be created to exclude sections of the book from your "
"normal reading flow:\n"
"- hidden flows will automatically be skipped when turning pages within the "
"regular flow;\n"
"- pages part of hidden flows are assigned distinct page numbers and won't be "
"considered in the various book & chapter progress and time to read "
"features;\n"
"- following direct links to pages in hidden flows will still work, including "
"from the TOC or Book map.\n"
"\n"
"This can be useful to exclude long footnotes or bibliography sections.\n"
"It can also be handy when interested in reading only a subset of a book.\n"
"\n"
"In Page browser, you can long-press on a thumbnail to start a hidden flow or "
"restart the regular flow on this page.\n"
"(Once you're done building it and don't want to see the button anymore, you "
"can disable Edit mode.)\n"
"\n"
"Hidden flows are shown with gray or hatched background in Book map and Page "
"browser."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir sreafaí folaithe saincheaptha a chruthú chun codanna den leabhar a "
"eisiamh ó do shreabhadh léitheoireachta gnáth:\n"
"- scipeálfar sreafaí folaithe go huathoibríoch agus leathanaigh á gcasadh "
"laistigh den shreabhadh rialta;\n"
"- sanntar uimhreacha leathanaigh ar leith do leathanaigh atá mar chuid de "
"shreafaí folaithe agus ní chuirfear san áireamh iad sna gnéithe éagsúla dul "
"chun cinn leabhar & caibidlí agus ama le léamh;\n"
"- oibreoidh naisc dhíreacha chuig leathanaigh i sreafaí folaithe fós, lena n-"
"áirítear ón TOC nó ón léarscáil Leabhar.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leis seo a bheith úsáideach chun nótaí fada nó codanna "
"leabharliosta a eisiamh.\n"
"Is féidir leis a bheith áisiúil freisin nuair is spéis leat fo-thacar de "
"leabhar amháin a léamh.\n"
"\n"
"Sa bhrabhsálaí leathanaigh, is féidir leat brú fada a chur ar mhionsamhail "
"chun sreabhadh folaithe a thosú nó an sreabhadh rialta a atosú ar an "
"leathanach seo.\n"
"(Nuair a bheidh tú críochnaithe leis agus mura dteastaíonn uait an cnaipe a "
"fheiceáil a thuilleadh, is féidir leat mód Eagarthóireachta a dhíchumasú.)\n"
"\n"
"Taispeántar sreafaí folaithe le cúlra liath nó grinnithe sa Léarscáil "
"Leabhar agus sa bhrabhsálaí leathanaigh."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:248
msgid "Clear inactive marked pages (%1)"
msgstr "Glan leathanaigh mharcáilte neamhghníomhacha (%1)"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:255
msgid ""
"Inactive marked pages are pages that you tagged as start hidden flow or "
"restart regular flow, but that other marked pages made them have no effect.\n"
"Are you sure you want to clear them?"
msgstr ""
"Is leathanaigh iad leathanaigh mharcáilte neamhghníomhacha ar a bhfuil clib "
"déanta agat mar \"tosaigh sreabhadh i bhfolach\" nó \"atosaigh sreabhadh "
"rialta\", ach nach raibh aon éifeacht ag baint leo mar gheall ar leathanaigh "
"mharcáilte eile.\n"
"An bhfuil tú cinnte gur mhaith leat iad a ghlanadh?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhandmade.lua:275
msgid "Clear all marked pages"
msgstr "Glan na leathanaigh mharcáilte go léir"

