"highlights into a PDF modifies the file which may change the partial hash, "
"resulting in its metadata (e.g., highlights and progress) being unlinked and "
"lost."
msgstr ""
"Rabhadh: Tá suíomh meiteashonraí an leabhair socraithe go stóráil bunaithe "
"ar hais. Athraítear an comhad nuair a scríobhtar buaicphointí i PDF, rud a "
"d’fhéadfadh an hais pháirteach a athrú, rud a fhágann go ndínascfar agus go "
"gcaillfear a mheiteashonraí (e.g., buaicphointí agus dul chun cinn)."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:612
