msgid "Reader"
msgstr "Léitheoir"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:855
msgid "Crosshairs speed"
msgstr "Luas na gcrosairí"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:856
msgid ""
"Select a decimal value from 0.25 to 5. A smaller value increases the travel "
"distance of the crosshairs per keystroke. Font size and this value are "
"inversely correlated, meaning a smaller font size requires a larger value "
"and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh luach deachúil ó 0.25 go 5. Méadaíonn luach níos lú an fad taistil "
"a bhíonn ag na crosairí in aghaidh gach brú eochrach. Tá comhghaol "
"inbhéartach idir méid an chló agus an luach seo, rud a chiallaíonn go n-"
"éilíonn méid cló níos lú luach níos mó agus a mhalairt."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:867
msgid "Increase crosshairs speed on consecutive keystrokes"
msgstr "Méadaigh luas na gcrosairí ar bhrúnna eochracha as a chéile"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:881
msgid "Interval for crosshairs speed increase: 1 second"
msgid_plural "Interval for crosshairs speed increase: %1 seconds"
msgstr[0] "Eatramh le haghaidh méadú ar luas na gcrosairí: 1 soicind"
msgstr[1] "Interval for crosshairs speed increase: %1 soicindí"
msgstr[2] "Interval for crosshairs speed increase: %1 soicindí"
msgstr[3] "Interval for crosshairs speed increase: %1 soicindí"
msgstr[4] "Interval for crosshairs speed increase: %1 soicindí"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:896
msgid "Time interval"
msgstr "Eatramh ama"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:897
msgid ""
"Select a decimal value up to 1 second. This defines the time period within "
"which multiple keystrokes will trigger an increase in the crosshairs speed."
msgstr ""
"Roghnaigh luach deachúil suas le 1 soicind. Sainmhíníonn sé seo an tréimhse "
"ama ina spreagfaidh il-bhuillí eochair méadú ar luas na crosaire."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:910
msgid "Text selection tools"
msgstr "Uirlisí roghnúcháin téacs"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:918
msgid "Multi-word selection: %1"
msgstr "Rogha ilfhoclach: %1"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:937
#: frontend/dispatcher.lua:211
msgid "Translate current page"
msgstr "Aistrigh an leathanach reatha"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:947
msgid "Allow panel zoom"
msgstr "Ceadaigh súmáil an phainéil"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:962
msgid "Fall back to text selection"
msgstr "Fill ar ais go dtí roghnú téacs"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1026
msgid ""
"You are currently in SELECT mode.\n"
"To finish highlighting, long press where the highlight should end and press "
"the HIGHLIGHT button.\n"
"You can also exit select mode by tapping on the start of the highlight."
msgstr ""
"Tá tú i mód ROGHNAITHE faoi láthair.\n"
"Chun críoch a chur leis an aibhsiú, brúigh go fada san áit ar cheart don "
"aibhsiú críochnú agus brúigh an cnaipe HIGHLIGHT.\n"
"Is féidir leat imeacht ón mód roghnaithe freisin trí thapáil ar thús an "
"aibhsithe."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1350
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1442
msgid "Note"
msgstr "Nóta"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1384
msgid "Delete highlight"
msgstr "Scrios aibhsigh"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1391
msgid "Highlight menu"
msgstr "Roghchlár aibhsithe"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1427
msgctxt "Highlight"
msgid "Style"
msgstr "Stíl"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1434
msgctxt "Highlight"
msgid "Color"
msgstr "Dath"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1449
msgid "Details"
msgstr "Sonraí"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:1950
msgid ""
"No OCR results or no language data.\n"
"\n"
"KOReader has a built-in OCR engine for recognizing words in scanned PDF and "
"DjVu documents. In order to use OCR in scanned pages, you need to install "
"tesseract trained data for your document language.\n"
"\n"
"You can download language data files for Tesseract version 5.3.4 from "
"https://tesseract-ocr.github.io/tessdoc/Data-Files\n"
"\n"
"Copy the language data files (e.g., eng.traineddata for English and "
"spa.traineddata for Spanish) into koreader/data/tessdata"
msgstr ""
"Gan aon torthaí OCR ná gan aon sonraí teanga.\n"
"\n"
"Tá inneall OCR ionsuite ag KOReader chun focail a aithint i ndoiciméid PDF "
"agus DjVu scanta. Chun OCR a úsáid i leathanaigh scanta, ní mór duit sonraí "
"oilte tesseract a shuiteáil do theanga do dhoiciméid.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat comhaid sonraí teanga a íoslódáil do Tesseract leagan 5.3.4 ó "
"https://tesseract-ocr.github.io/tessdoc/Data-Files\n"
"\n"
"Cóipeáil na comhaid sonraí teanga (m.sh., eng.traineddata don Bhéarla agus "
"spa.traineddata don Spáinnis) isteach i koreader/data/tessdata"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:2150
msgid "Default highlight action changed to '%1'."
msgstr "Athraíodh an gníomh réamhshocraithe aibhsithe go '%1'."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerhighlight.lua:2198
msgid "Default highlight style changed to '%1'."
msgstr "Athraíodh an stíl réamhshocraithe aibhsithe go '%1'."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:155
msgid "Show QR code"
msgstr "Taispeáin cód QR"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:168
msgid "Open in browser"
msgstr "Oscail sa bhrabhsálaí"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:182
msgid "Read online"
msgstr "Léigh ar líne"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:194
msgid ""
"Would you like to read this Wikipedia %1 article?\n"
"\n"
"%2\n"
msgstr ""
"Ar mhaith leat an t-alt Vicipéide %1 seo a léamh?\n"
"\n"
"%2\n"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:204
msgid "Read EPUB"
msgstr "Léigh EPUB"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:215
msgid ""
"This article has previously been saved as EPUB. You may wish to read the "
"saved EPUB instead."
msgstr ""
"Sábháladh an t-alt seo mar EPUB roimhe seo. B’fhéidir gur mhaith leat an "
"EPUB sábháilte a léamh ina ionad."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:321
msgid "Show footnotes in popup"
msgstr "Taispeáin nótaí coise i bpreabfhuinneog"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:330
msgid ""
"Show internal link target content in a footnote popup when it looks like it "
"might be a footnote, instead of following the link.\n"
"\n"
"Note that depending on the book quality, footnote detection may not always "
"work correctly.\n"
"The footnote content may be empty, truncated, or include other footnotes.\n"
"\n"
"From the footnote popup, you can jump to the footnote location in the book "
"by swiping to the left."
msgstr ""
"Taispeáin ábhar sprice an naisc inmheánaigh i bhfuinneog nótaí coise aníos "
"nuair a bhíonn cuma air gur nóta coise é, seachas an nasc a leanúint.\n"
"\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara, ag brath ar cháilíocht an leabhair, nach n-oibreoidh "
"braiteadh nótaí coise i gceart i gcónaí.\n"
"D’fhéadfadh ábhar an nóta coise a bheith folamh, gearrtha, nó nótaí coise "
"eile a bheith ann.\n"
"\n"
"Ón bhfuinneog nótaí coise aníos, is féidir leat léim go dtí suíomh an nóta "
"coise sa leabhar trí shlaodadh ar chlé."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:343
msgid "Show more links as footnotes"
msgstr "Taispeáin níos mó nasc mar nótaí coise"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:353
msgid "Loosen footnote detection rules to show more links as footnotes."
msgstr ""
"Scaoil rialacha braite nótaí coise chun níos mó nasc a thaispeáint mar nótaí "
"coise."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:357
msgid "Use book font in popups"
msgstr "Úsáid cló leabhar i bhfuinneoga aníos"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:368
msgid ""
"Display the footnote popup text with the configured document font (the book "
"text may still render with a different font if the book uses embedded fonts)."
msgstr ""
"Taispeáin téacs an fho-nóta leis an gcló cumraithe don doiciméad (féadfaidh "
"téacs an leabhair a bheith rindreáilte le cló difriúil fós má úsáideann an "
"leabhar clónna leabaithe)."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:371
msgid "Footnote popup font size"
msgstr "Méid cló aníos nóta coise"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:390
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:412
msgid "Set font size"
msgstr "Socraigh méid an chló"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:391
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:413
msgid "Set footnote popup font size"
msgstr "Socraigh méid cló aníos nóta coise"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:392
msgid ""
"The footnote popup font can adjust to the font size you've set for the "
"document, but you can specify here a fixed absolute font size to be used "
"instead."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir cló an fho-nóta aníos a choigeartú de réir mhéid an chló atá "
"socraithe agat don doiciméad, ach is féidir leat méid cló seasta "
"absalóideach a shonrú anseo le húsáid ina ionad."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:398
msgid "Set a relative font size instead"
msgstr "Socraigh méid cló coibhneasta ina ionad"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:414
msgid ""
"The footnote popup font adjusts to the font size you've set for the "
"document.\n"
"You can specify here how much smaller or larger it should be relative to the "
"document font size.\n"
"A negative value will make it smaller, while a positive one will make it "
"larger.\n"
"The recommended value is -2."
msgstr ""
"Athraíonn cló an fhonóta aníos de réir mhéid an chló atá socraithe agat don "
"doiciméad.\n"
"Is féidir leat a shonrú anseo cé mhéad níos lú nó níos mó ba chóir dó a "
"bheith i gcoibhneas le méid cló an doiciméid.\n"
"Déanfaidh luach diúltach é níos lú, agus déanfaidh luach dearfach é níos "
"mó.\n"
"Is é -2 an luach molta."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:423
msgid "Set an absolute font size instead"
msgstr "Socraigh méid cló iomlán ina ionad sin"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:437
msgid ""
"The footnote popup font adjusts to the font size you've set for the "
"document.\n"
"This allows you to specify how much smaller or larger it should be relative "
"to the document font size."
msgstr ""
"Athraíonn cló an fhonóta aníos de réir mhéid an chló atá socraithe agat don "
"doiciméad.\n"
"Ligeann sé seo duit a shonrú cé mhéad níos lú nó níos mó ba chóir dó a "
"bheith i gcoibhneas le méid cló an doiciméid."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:453
msgid "Footnote popup settings"
msgstr "Socruithe aníos nótaí coise"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:468
msgid "Go back to previous location"
msgstr "Téigh ar ais go dtí an suíomh roimhe seo"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:473
msgid "Clear location history?"
msgstr "Scrios stair na suíomhanna?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:483
msgid "Go forward to next location"
msgstr "Téigh ar aghaidh go dtí an chéad suíomh eile"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:488
msgid "Clear forward location history?"
msgstr "Scrios stair suíomhanna ar aghaidh?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:502
msgid "Footnotes and links"
msgstr "Nótaí coise agus naisc"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:510
#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:651
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Naisc"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:513
msgid "Tap to follow links"
msgstr "Tapáil chun naisc a leanúint"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:519
msgid "Tap on links to follow them."
msgstr "Tapáil ar naisc chun iad a leanúint."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:522
msgid "Ignore external links on tap"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de naisc sheachtracha ar an toirt"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:529
msgid ""
"Ignore taps on external links. Useful with Wikipedia EPUBs to make page "
"turning easier.\n"
"You can still follow them from the dictionary window or the selection menu "
"after holding on them."
msgstr ""
"Déan neamhaird de thapaí ar naisc sheachtracha. Úsáideach le EPUBanna "
"Vicipéide chun casadh leathanaigh a dhéanamh níos éasca.\n"
"Is féidir leat leanúint orthu fós ón bhfuinneog foclóra nó ón roghchlár "
"roghnúcháin tar éis duit iad a shealbhú."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:535
msgid "Swipe to go back"
msgstr "Swipeáil le dul ar ais"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:541
msgid ""
"Swipe to the right to go back to the previous location after you have "
"followed a link. When the location stack is empty, swiping to the right "
"takes you to the previous page."
msgstr ""
"Svaidhpeáil ar dheis chun filleadh ar an suíomh roimhe seo tar éis duit nasc "
"a leanúint. Nuair a bhíonn an carn suíomhanna folamh, tabharfaidh "
"svaidhpeáil ar dheis chuig an leathanach roimhe seo thú."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:544
msgid "Swipe to follow nearest link"
msgstr "Svaidhpeáil chun an nasc is gaire a leanúint"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:550
msgid ""
"Swipe to the left to follow the link nearest to where you started the swipe. "
"This is useful when a small font is used and tapping on small links is "
"tedious."
msgstr ""
"Svaidhpeáil ar chlé chun an nasc is gaire don áit ar thosaigh tú an "
"svaidhpeáil a leanúint. Tá sé seo úsáideach nuair a úsáidtear cló beag agus "
"nuair a bhíonn sé leadránach tapáil ar naisc bheaga."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:553
msgid "Ignore external links on swipe"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de naisc sheachtracha ar shlaipeadh"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:560
msgid ""
"Ignore external links near swipe. Useful with Wikipedia EPUBs to follow only "
"footnotes with swipe.\n"
"You can still follow external links from the dictionary window or the "
"selection menu after holding on them."
msgstr ""
"Déan neamhaird de naisc sheachtracha in aice le svaidhpeáil. Úsáideach le "
"EPUBanna Vicipéide chun nótaí coise amháin a leanúint le svaidhpeáil.\n"
"Is féidir leat naisc sheachtracha a leanúint fós ón bhfuinneog foclóra nó ón "
"roghchlár roghnúcháin tar éis duit iad a choinneáil siar."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:566
msgid "Swipe to jump to latest bookmark"
msgstr "Svaidhpeáil chun léim go dtí an leabharmharc is déanaí"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:572
msgid ""
"Swipe to the left to go the most recently bookmarked page.\n"
"This can be useful to quickly swipe back and forth between what you are "
"reading and some reference page (for example notes, a map or a characters "
"list).\n"
"If any of the other Swipe to follow link options is enabled, this will work "
"only when the current page contains no link."
msgstr ""
"Svaidhpeáil ar chlé chun dul chuig an leathanach is déanaí a bhfuil "
"leabharmharc curtha leis.\n"
"Is féidir leis seo a bheith úsáideach chun svaidhpeáil go tapa ar ais agus "
"amach idir an méid atá á léamh agat agus leathanach tagartha éigin (mar "
"shampla nótaí, léarscáil nó liosta carachtar).\n"
"Má tá aon cheann de na roghanna nasc Svaidhpeáil chun leanúint cumasaithe, "
"ní oibreoidh sé seo ach amháin nuair nach bhfuil nasc ar an leathanach "
"reatha."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:587
msgid "Allow larger tap area around links"
msgstr "Ceadaigh limistéar sconna níos mó timpeall naisc"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:594
msgid ""
"Extends the tap area around internal links. Useful with a small font where "
"tapping on small footnote links may be tedious."
msgstr ""
"Leathnaíonn sé seo an limistéar tapála timpeall naisc inmheánacha. Úsáideach "
"le cló beag nuair a d’fhéadfadh sé a bheith leadránach tapáil ar naisc "
"bheaga nótaí."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:747
msgid "Tap to follow links: %1"
msgstr "Tapáil chun naisc a leanúint: %1"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:774
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:781
msgid "Current location added to history."
msgstr "Cuireadh an suíomh reatha leis an stair."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:801
msgid "Location history cleared."
msgstr "Glanadh stair na suíomhanna."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:847
msgid "Link from page %1"
msgstr "Nasc ó leathanach %1"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:913
msgid ""
"Invalid or external link:\n"
"%1"
msgstr ""
"Nasc neamhbhailí nó seachtrach:\n"
"%1"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:962
msgid ""
"Would you like to read this local document?\n"
"\n"
"%1\n"
msgstr ""
"Ar mhaith leat an doiciméad áitiúil seo a léamh?\n"
"\n"
"%1\n"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerlink.lua:1620
msgid ""
"External link:\n"
"\n"
"%1"
msgstr ""
"Nasc seachtrach:\n"
"\n"
"%1"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:194
msgid "Document settings"
msgstr "Socruithe doiciméad"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:197
msgid "Reset document settings to default"
msgstr "Athshocraigh socruithe doiciméad go dtí na socruithe réamhshocraithe"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:201
msgid ""
"Reset current document settings to their default values?\n"
"\n"
"Reading position, highlights and bookmarks will be kept.\n"
"The document will be reloaded."
msgstr ""
"Athshocraigh socruithe reatha an doiciméid go dtí a luachanna "
"réamhshocraithe?\n"
"\n"
"Coinneofar suíomh léitheoireachta, aibhsithe agus leabharmharcanna.\n"
"Athlódálfar an doiciméad."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:214
msgid "Save document settings as default"
msgstr "Sábháil socruithe an doiciméid mar réamhshocrú"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:219
msgid "Save current document settings as default values?"
msgstr "Sábháil socruithe reatha an doiciméid mar luachanna réamhshocraithe?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:225
msgid "Default settings updated"
msgstr "Socruithe réamhshocraithe nuashonraithe"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:239
#: frontend/ui/elements/page_turns.lua:170
msgid "Invert document-related dialogs"
msgstr "Inbhéartaigh dialóga a bhaineann le doiciméid"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:255
#: frontend/ui/elements/page_turns.lua:186
msgid ""
"The default (★) for newly opened books is to Invert document-related "
"dialogs.\n"
"\n"
"Would you like to change it?"
msgstr ""
"Is é an réamhshocrú (★) do leabhair nua-oscailte ná dialóga a bhaineann le "
"doiciméid a aisiompú.\n"
"\n"
"Ar mhaith leat é a athrú?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:256
#: frontend/ui/elements/page_turns.lua:187
msgid ""
"The default (★) for newly opened books is not to Invert document-related "
"dialogs.\n"
"\n"
"Would you like to change it?"
msgstr ""
"Ní hé an rogha réamhshocraithe (★) do leabhair nua-oscailte ná dialóga a "
"bhaineann le doiciméid a aisiompú.\n"
"\n"
"Ar mhaith leat é a athrú?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:258
#: frontend/ui/elements/page_turns.lua:189
msgid "Don't invert"
msgstr "Ná déan inbhéartú"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:273
#: frontend/ui/elements/page_turns.lua:204
msgid ""
"When enabled the UI direction for the Table of Contents, Book Map, and Page "
"Browser dialogs will mirror the default UI direction.\n"
"Useful when used alongside 'Invert page turn taps and swipes'."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh sé cumasaithe, léireofar treo an chomhéadain úsáideora do na "
"dialóga Clár Ábhair, Léarscáil Leabhar, agus Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh an treo "
"réamhshocraithe den chomhéadan úsáideora.\n"
"Úsáideach nuair a úsáidtear é in éineacht le 'Inbhéartaigh sconnaí agus "
"svaidhpeálacha casadh leathanaigh'."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:304
msgid "Do not show this book cover on sleep screen"
msgstr "Ná taispeáin clúdach an leabhair seo ar an scáileán codlata"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:348 frontend/dispatcher.lua:59
msgid "Open previous document"
msgstr "Oscail an doiciméad roimhe seo"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readermenu.lua:351
