#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readersearch.lua:54
msgid ""
"Regular expressions allow you to search for a matching pattern in a text. "
"The simplest pattern is a simple sequence of characters, such as `James "
"Bond`. There are many different varieties of regular expressions, but we "
"support the ECMAScript syntax. The basics will be explained below.\n"
"\n"
"If you want to search for all occurrences of 'Mister Moore', 'Sir Moore' or "
"'Alfons Moore' but not for 'Lady Moore'.\n"
"Enter 'Mister Moore|Sir Moore|Alfons Moore'.\n"
"\n"
"If your search contains a special character from ^$.*+?()[]{}|\\/ you have "
"to put a \\ before that character.\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"Words containing 'os' -> '[^ ]+os[^ ]+'\n"
"Any single character '.' -> 'r.nge'\n"
"Any characters '.*' -> 'J.*s'\n"
"Numbers -> '[0-9]+'\n"
"Character range -> '[a-f]'\n"
"Not a space -> '[^ ]'\n"
"A word -> '[^ ]*[^ ]'\n"
"Last word in a sentence -> '[^ ]*\\.'\n"
"\n"
"Complex expressions may lead to an extremely long search time, in which case "
"not all matches will be shown."
msgstr ""
"Le habairtí rialta is féidir leat patrún comhoiriúnach a chuardach i dtéacs. "
"Is é an patrún is simplí ná seicheamh simplí carachtar, amhail `James Bond`. "
"Tá go leor cineálacha éagsúla de habairtí rialta ann, ach tacaímid le "
"comhréir ECMAScript. Míneofar na bunghnéithe thíos.\n"
"\n"
"Más mian leat cuardach a dhéanamh ar gach cás de 'Mister Moore', 'Sir Moore' "
"nó 'Alfons Moore' ach ní ar 'Lady Moore'.\n"
"Iontráil 'Mister Moore|Sir Moore|Alfons Moore'.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá carachtar speisialta ó ^$.*+?()[]{}|\\/ i do chuardach, ní mór duit \\ "
"a chur roimh an gcarachtar sin.\n"
"\n"
"Samplaí:\n"
"Focail ina bhfuil 'os' -> '[^ ]+os[^ ]+'\n"
"Aon charachtar aonair '.' -> 'r.nge'\n"
"Aon charachtair '.*' -> 'J.*s'\n"
"Uimhreacha -> '[0-9]+'\n"
"Raon carachtar -> '[a-f]'\n"
"Ní spás é -> '[^ ]'\n"
"Focal -> '[^ ]*[^ ]'\n"
"An focal deireanach in abairt -> '[^ ]*\\.'\n"
"\n"
"D’fhéadfadh am cuardaigh thar a bheith fada a bheith mar thoradh ar nathanna "
"casta, agus sa chás sin ní thaispeánfar gach meaitseáil."

