#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:848
msgid "You can add CSS snippets which will be applied only to this book."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat sleachta CSS a chur leis nach gcuirfear i bhfeidhm ach ar an "
"leabhar seo."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:851
msgid "Long-press for info ⓘ"
msgstr "Brúigh go fada le haghaidh eolais ⓘ"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:851
msgid ""
"This menu provides a non-exhaustive CSS syntax and properties list. It also "
"shows some KOReader-specific, non-standard CSS features that can be useful "
"with e-books.\n"
"\n"
"Most of these bits are already used by our categorized 'Style tweaks' (found "
"in the top menu). Long-press on any style-tweak option to see its code and "
"its expected results. Should these not be enough to achieve your desired "
"look, you may need to adjust them slightly: tap once on the CSS code-box to "
"copy the code to the clipboard, paste it here and edit it.\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on any item in this popup to get more information on what it does "
"and what it can help solving.\n"
"\n"
"Tap on the item to insert it: you can then edit it and combine it with "
"others."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an roghchlár seo liosta neamh-uileghabhálach de chomhréir agus "
"airíonna CSS ar fáil. Taispeánann sé freisin roinnt gnéithe CSS "
"neamhchaighdeánacha, atá sainiúil do KOReader agus a d'fhéadfadh a bheith "
"úsáideach le ríomhleabhair.\n"
"\n"
"Tá an chuid is mó de na píosaí seo in úsáid cheana féin ag ár 'Coigeartuithe "
"Stíl' catagóirithe (atá le fáil sa roghchlár barr). Brúigh fada ar aon rogha "
"coigeartaithe stíl chun a chód agus a thorthaí ionchais a fheiceáil. Mura "
"leor iad seo chun an cuma atá uait a bhaint amach, b'fhéidir go mbeidh ort "
"iad a choigeartú beagán: sconna uair amháin ar an mbosca cód CSS chun an cód "
"a chóipeáil chuig an ghearrthaisce, greamaigh anseo é agus cuir in eagar é.\n"
"\n"
"Brúigh fada ar aon mhír sa bhfuinneog aníos seo chun tuilleadh eolais a "
"fháil ar a ndéanann sé agus ar na rudaí is féidir leis cabhrú leo a "
"réiteach.\n"
"\n"
"Sconnaigh ar an mír chun í a chur isteach: is féidir leat í a chur in eagar "
"agus í a chomhcheangal le cinn eile ansin."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:860
msgid "Matching elements"
msgstr "Eilimintí comhoiriúnacha"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:861
msgid ""
"p.className matches a <p> with class='className'.\n"
"\n"
"*.className matches any element with class='className'.\n"
"\n"
"p:not([class]) matches a <p> without any class= attribute."
msgstr ""
"Meaitseálann p.className <p> le class='className'.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann *.className aon eilimint le class='className'.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p:not([class]) <p> gan aon tréith class=."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:867
msgid ""
"aside > p matches a <p> children of an <aside> element.\n"
"\n"
"aside p (without any intermediate symbol) matches a <p> descendant of an "
"<aside> element."
msgstr ""
"Meaitseálann aside > p clann <p> d'eilimint <aside>.\n"
"\n"
"meaitseálann aside p (gan aon siombail idirmheánach) sliocht <p> d'eilimint "
"<aside>."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:871
msgid ""
"p + img matches a <img> if its immediate previous sibling is a <p>.\n"
"\n"
"p ~ img matches a <img> if any of its previous siblings is a <p>."
msgstr ""
"Meaitseálann p + img <img> má tá a dheartháir díreach roimhe ina <p>.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p ~ img <img> má tá aon cheann dá dheartháireacha roimhe seo "
"ina <p>."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:876
msgid ""
"[name=\"what\"] matches if the element has the attribute 'name' and its "
"value is exactly 'what'.\n"
"\n"
"[name] matches if the attribute 'name' is present.\n"
"\n"
"[name~=\"what\"] matches if the value of the attribute 'name' contains "
"'what' as a word (among other words separated by spaces)."
msgstr ""
"Meaitseálann [name=\"what\"] má tá an tréith 'name' ag an eilimint agus má "
"tá a luach díreach mar 'what'.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann [name] má tá an tréith 'name' i láthair.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann [name~=\"what\"] má tá 'what' mar fhocal i luach na tréithe "
"'name' (i measc focal eile scartha le spásanna)."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:883
msgid ""
"[name*=\"what\" i] matches any element having the attribute 'name' with a "
"value that contains 'what', case insensitive.\n"
"\n"
"[name^=\"what\"] matches if the attribute value starts with 'what'.\n"
"\n"
"[name$=\"what\"] matches if the attribute value ends with 'what'."
msgstr ""
"Meaitseálann [name*=\"what\" i] aon eilimint a bhfuil an tréith 'name' aici "
"le luach ina bhfuil 'what', gan cás-íogaireacht.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann [name^=\"what\"] má thosaíonn luach na tréithe le 'what'.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann [name$=\"what\"] má chríochnaíonn luach na tréithe le 'what'."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:890
msgid ""
"Similar in syntax to attribute matching, but matches the inner text of an "
"element.\n"
"\n"
"p[_=\"what\"] matches any <p> whose text is exactly 'what'.\n"
"\n"
"p[_] matches any non-empty <p>.\n"
"\n"
"p:not([_]) matches any empty <p>.\n"
"\n"
"p[_~=\"what\"] matches any <p> that contains the word 'what'."
msgstr ""
"Cosúil ó thaobh comhréir de le meaitseáil tréithe, ach meaitseálann sé téacs "
"istigh eiliminte.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p[_=\"cad\"] aon <p> a bhfuil a théacs díreach 'cad'.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p[_] aon <p> neamh-fholamh.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p:not([_]) aon <p> folamh.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p[_~=\"cad\"] aon <p> ina bhfuil an focal 'cad'."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:901
msgid ""
"Similar in syntax to attribute matching, but matches the inner text of an "
"element.\n"
"\n"
"p[_*=\"what\" i] matches any <p> that contains 'what', case insensitive.\n"
"\n"
"p[_^=\"what\"] matches any <p> whose text starts with 'what'.\n"
"(This can be used to match \"Act\" or \"Scene\", or character names in "
"plays, and make them stand out.)\n"
"\n"
"p[_$=\"what\"] matches any <p> whose text ends with 'what'."
msgstr ""
"Cosúil ó thaobh comhréir de le meaitseáil tréithe, ach meaitseálann sé téacs "
"inmheánach eiliminte.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p[_*=\"cad\" i] aon <p> ina bhfuil 'cad', gan cás-íogaireacht.\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p[_^=\"cad\"] aon <p> a thosaíonn a théacs le 'cad'.\n"
"(Is féidir é seo a úsáid chun \"Acht\" nó \"Radharc\" a mheaitseáil, nó "
"ainmneacha carachtar i ndrámaí, agus iad a chur chun cinn.)\n"
"\n"
"Meaitseálann p[_$=\"cad\"] aon <p> a chríochnaíonn a théacs le 'cad'."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:911
msgid ""
"p:first-child matches a <p> that is the first child of its parent.\n"
"\n"
"p:last-child matches a <p> that is the last child of its parent.\n"
"\n"
"p:nth-child(odd) matches any other <p> in a series of sibling <p>."
msgstr ""
"p:comhionann le <p> arb é an chéad leanbh dá thuismitheoir é.\n"
"\n"
"p:comhionann le <p> arb é an leanbh deireanach dá thuismitheoir é.\n"
"\n"
"p:nth-child(corr)comhionann le haon <p> eile i sraith de <p> siblíní."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:918
msgid ""
"On a book page, select some text spanning around (before and after) the "
"element you are interested in, and use 'View HTML'.\n"
"In the HTML viewer, long press on tags or text to get a list of selectors "
"matching the element: tap on one of them to copy it to the clipboard.\n"
"You can then paste it here with long-press in the text box."
msgstr ""
"Ar leathanach leabhair, roghnaigh téacs a shíneann timpeall (roimh agus i "
"ndiaidh) an eilimint a bhfuil suim agat ann, agus bain úsáid as 'Féach ar "
"HTML'.\n"
"Sa bhreathnóir HTML, brúigh ar chlibeanna nó ar théacs chun liosta roghnóirí "
"a fháil a mheaitseálann an eilimint: tapáil ar cheann acu chun é a chóipeáil "
"chuig an ghearrthaisce.\n"
"Ansin is féidir leat é a ghreamú anseo le brú ar an mbosca téacs."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:925
msgid "Common classic properties"
msgstr "Airíonna clasaiceacha coitianta"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:926
msgid "1rem will enforce your main font size."
msgstr "Cuirfidh 1rem do phríomhmhéid cló i bhfeidhm."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:927
msgid "Remove bold. Use 'bold' to get bold."
msgstr "Bain an cló trom. Úsáid 'trom' chun é a dhéanamh trom."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:928
msgid "Disables hyphenation inside the targeted elements."
msgstr "Díchumasaíonn sé fleiscíniú laistigh de na heilimintí spriocdhírithe."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:929
msgid "1.2em is our default text indentation."
msgstr "Is é 1.2em ár n-eangach téacs réamhshocraithe."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:930
msgid "Start a new page with this element. Use 'avoid' to avoid a new page."
msgstr ""
"Tosaigh leathanach nua leis an eilimint seo. Bain úsáid as 'seachain' chun "
"leathanach nua a sheachaint."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:931
msgid "Force text to be black."
msgstr "Éirigh le téacs a bheith dubh."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:932
msgid "Remove any background color."
msgstr "Bain aon dath cúlra."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:933
msgid ""
"Limit an element width to 50% of your screen width (use 'max-height: 50vh' "
"for 50% of the screen height). Can be useful with <img> to limit their size."
msgstr ""
"Cuir teorainn le leithead eiliminte go 50% de leithead do scáileáin (bain "
"úsáid as 'max-height: 50vh' le haghaidh 50% d'airde an scáileáin). Is féidir "
"é seo a úsáid le <img> chun a méid a theorannú."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:936
msgid "Private CSS properties"
msgstr "Airíonna CSS príobháideacha"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:937
msgid ""
"When set on a block element containing the target id of a href, this block "
"element will be shown as an in-page footnote."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shocrófar é ar eilimint bhloc ina bhfuil aitheantas sprice href, "
"taispeánfar an eilimint bhloc seo mar fhonóta sa leathanach."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:938
msgid ""
"When set on a block element following a block element marked `footnote-"
"inpage`, this block will be shown as part of the same in-page footnote as "
"the previous element. Can be chained across multiple elements following an "
"in-page footnote."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shocraítear é ar eilimint bhloc i ndiaidh eilimint bhloc atá "
"marcáilte mar `footnote-inpage`, taispeánfar an bloc seo mar chuid den "
"fhonóta céanna sa leathanach leis an eilimint roimhe sin. Is féidir é a "
"shlabhrú trasna il-eilimintí i ndiaidh fonóta sa leathanach."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:939
msgid ""
"Can be set on some specific DocFragments (e.g. DocFragment[id$=_16]) to "
"ignore them in the linear pages flow."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir é seo a shocrú ar roinnt DocFragments sonracha (e.g. "
"DocFragment[id$=_16]) chun neamhaird a dhéanamh orthu i sreabhadh líneach na "
"leathanach."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:940
msgid ""
"Can be set on contiguous footnote blocks to ignore them in the linear pages "
"flow."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir é a shocrú ar bhloic nótaí comhleanúnacha chun neamhaird a "
"dhéanamh orthu i sreabhadh líneach na leathanach."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:941
msgid ""
"When set on an element, its text can be used to build the alternative table "
"of contents. toc-level2 to toc-level6 can be used for nested chapters."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shocraítear é ar eilimint, is féidir a théacs a úsáid chun an clár "
"ábhair malartach a thógáil. Is féidir toc-level2 go toc-level6 a úsáid le "
"haghaidh caibidlí neadaithe."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:942
msgid ""
"When set on an element, it will be ignored when building the alternative "
"table of contents."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a shocrófar é ar eilimint, déanfar neamhaird de agus an clár ábhair "
"malartach á thógáil."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:943
msgid ""
"Can be set on target of links (<div id='..'>) to have their link trigger as "
"footnote popup, in case KOReader wrongly detect this target is not a "
"footnote."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir é seo a shocrú ar sprioc na nasc (<div id='..'>) chun a nasc a "
"spreagadh mar fhonóta aníos, i gcás go mbraitheann KOReader go mícheart nach "
"fonóta an sprioc seo."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:944
msgid ""
"Can be set on links (<a href='#..'>) to have them trigger as footnote "
"popups, in case KOReader wrongly detect the links is not to a footnote."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir é seo a shocrú ar naisc (<a href='#..'>) chun iad a spreagadh mar "
"fhuinneoga aníos i bhfonótaí, i gcás go mbraitheann KOReader go mícheart "
"nach bhfuil na naisc chuig fonóta."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:945
msgid ""
"Can be set on links (<a href='#..'>) to have them NOT trigger footnote "
"popups and in-page footnotes.\n"
"If some DocFragment presents an index of names with cross references, "
"resulting in in-page footnotes taking half of these pages, you can avoid "
"this with:\n"
"DocFragment[id$=_16] a { -cr-hint: noteref-ignore }"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir é seo a shocrú ar naisc (<a href='#..'>) ionas nach spreagfaidh "
"siad fuinneoga aníos nótaí coise agus nótaí coise sa leathanach.\n"
"Má chuireann roinnt DocFragment innéacs ainmneacha le tagairtí trasna i "
"láthair, rud a fhágann go nglacann nótaí coise sa leathanach leath de na "
"leathanaigh seo, is féidir leat é seo a sheachaint le:\n"
"DocFragment[id$=_16] a { -cr-hint: noteref-ignore }"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:951
msgid "Useful 'content:' values"
msgstr "Luachanna úsáideacha 'ábhar:'"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:952
msgid "Caution ⚠"
msgstr "Rabhadh ⚠"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:952
msgid ""
"Be careful with these: stick them to a proper discriminating selector, "
"like:\n"
"\n"
"span.specificClassName\n"
"\n"
"p[_*=\"keyword\" i]\n"
"\n"
"If used as-is, they will act on ALL elements!"
msgstr ""
"Bí cúramach leo seo: greamaigh iad le roghnóir idirdhealaitheach cuí, mar "
"shampla:\n"
"\n"
"span.specificClassName\n"
"\n"
"p[_*=\"keyword\" i]\n"
"\n"
"Má úsáidtear iad mar atá, gníomhóidh siad ar GACH eilimint!"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:960
msgid "Insert a visible space before an element."
msgstr "Cuir spás infheicthe isteach roimh eilimint."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:961
msgid ""
"Insert a visible non-breakable space before an element, so it sticks to "
"what's before."
msgstr ""
"Cuir spás infheicthe dobhriste isteach roimh eilimint, ionas go gcloífidh sé "
"leis an méid atá roimhe."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:962
msgid ""
"U+2060 WORD JOINER may act as a glue (like an invisible non-breakable space) "
"before an element, so it sticks to what's before."
msgstr ""
"Féadfaidh U+2060 WORD JOINER gníomhú mar gliú (cosúil le spás dofheicthe "
"neamh-bhriste) roimh eilimint, ionas go gcloíonn sé leis an méid atá roimhe."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:963
msgid ""
"U+200B ZERO WIDTH SPACE may allow a linebreak before an element, in case the "
"absence of any space prevents that."
msgstr ""
"Féadfaidh U+200B SPÁS NIALAIS LEITHEAD briseadh líne a cheadú roimh "
"eilimint, i gcás nach bhfuil aon spás ann a chuireann cosc air sin."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readerstyletweak.lua:964
msgid ""
"Insert the value of the attribute 'title' at start of an element content."
msgstr "Cuir luach an tréith 'teideal' isteach ag tús ábhar eiliminte."

