#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:73 frontend/dispatcher.lua:198
msgid "Table of contents"
msgstr "Clár ábhair"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1109
msgid "No results in table of contents"
msgstr "Gan aon torthaí sa chlár ábhair"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1209
msgid "Alternative table of contents"
msgstr "Clár ábhair malartach"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1211
msgid ""
"An alternative table of contents can be built from document headings <H1> to "
"<H6>.\n"
"If the document contains no headings, or all are ignored, the alternative "
"ToC will be built from document fragments and will point to the start of "
"each individual HTML file in the EPUB.\n"
"\n"
"Some of the headings can be ignored, and hints can be set to other non-"
"heading elements in a user style tweak, so they can be used as ToC items.\n"
"See Style tweaks → Miscellaneous → Alternative ToC hints."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir clár ábhair malartach a thógáil ó cheannteidil doiciméad <H1> go "
"<H6>.\n"
"Mura bhfuil aon cheannteidil sa doiciméad, nó má dhéantar neamhaird orthu "
"uile, tógfar an TOC malartach ó blúirí doiciméad agus pointeálfaidh sé tús "
"gach comhaid HTML aonair san EPUB.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir neamhaird a dhéanamh de chuid de na ceannteidil, agus is féidir "
"leideanna a shocrú d’eilimintí nach ceannteidil iad i gcoigeartú stíl "
"úsáideora, ionas gur féidir iad a úsáid mar mhíreanna TOC.\n"
"Féach Coigeartuithe Stíle → Ilghnéitheach → Leideanna TOC Malartacha."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1218
msgid ""
"To use the alternative ToC, disable your custom table of contents first."
msgstr ""
"Chun an ToC malartach a úsáid, díchumasaigh do chlár ábhair saincheaptha ar "
"dtús."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1232
msgid ""
"The table of contents for this book is currently an alternative one built "
"from the document headings.\n"
"Do you want to get back the original table of contents? (The book will be "
"reloaded.)"
msgstr ""
"Is clár ábhair malartach é clár ábhair an leabhair seo faoi láthair atá "
"tógtha ó cheannteidil an doiciméid.\n"
"Ar mhaith leat an clár ábhair bunaidh a fháil ar ais? (Athlódálfar an "
"leabhar.)"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1247
msgid ""
"Do you want to use an alternative table of contents built from the document "
"headings?"
msgstr ""
"Ar mhaith leat clár ábhair malartach a úsáid atá tógtha ó cheannteidil an "
"doiciméid?"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1274
msgid "1 entry at ToC depth %2"
msgid_plural "%1 entries at ToC depth %2"
msgstr[0] "1 iontráil ag doimhneacht ToC %2"
msgstr[1] "%1 iontrálacha ag doimhneacht ToC %2"
msgstr[2] "%1 iontrálacha ag doimhneacht ToC %2"
msgstr[3] "%1 iontrálacha ag doimhneacht ToC %2"
msgstr[4] "%1 iontrálacha ag doimhneacht ToC %2"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1296
msgid "Progress bars: 1 tick"
msgid_plural "Progress bars: %1 ticks"
msgstr[0] "Barraí dul chun cinn: 1 tic"
msgstr[1] "Barraí dul chun cinn: %1 tic"
msgstr[2] "Barraí dul chun cinn: %1 tic"
msgstr[3] "Barraí dul chun cinn: %1 tic"
msgstr[4] "Barraí dul chun cinn: %1 tic"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1298
msgid ""
"The progress bars in the footer and the skim dialog can become cramped when "
"the table of contents is complex. This allows you to restrict the number of "
"tick marks."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir go mbeidh na barraí dul chun cinn sa bhuntásc agus sa dialóg scime "
"plódaithe nuair a bhíonn an clár ábhair casta. Ligeann sé seo duit líon na "
"marcanna tic a theorannú."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1319
msgid "Bind chapter navigation to ticks"
msgstr "Ceangail nascleanúint caibidle le ticeanna"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1320
msgid ""
"Entries from ToC levels that are ignored in the progress bars will still be "
"used for chapter navigation and 'page/time left until next chapter' in the "
"footer.\n"
"Enabling this option will restrict chapter navigation to progress bar ticks."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidfear iontrálacha ó leibhéil na dTéarmaí Cinnte a ndéantar neamhaird "
"orthu sna barraí dul chun cinn fós le haghaidh nascleanúint caibidle agus "
"'leathanach/am fágtha go dtí an chéad chaibidil eile' sa bhuntásc.\n"
"Má chumasaítear an rogha seo, cuirfear srian le nascleanúint caibidle go "
"ticeanna barra dul chun cinn."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1335
msgid "Chapter titles from ticks only"
msgstr "Teidil chaibidle ó thicéid amháin"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1336
msgid ""
"Entries from ToC levels that are ignored in the progress bars will still be "
"used for displaying the title of the current chapter in the footer and in "
"bookmarks.\n"
"Enabling this option will restrict display to the chapter titles of progress "
"bar ticks."
msgstr ""
"Úsáidfear iontrálacha ó leibhéil ToC a ndéantar neamhaird orthu sna barraí "
"dul chun cinn fós chun teideal na caibidle reatha a thaispeáint sa bhuntásc "
"agus i leabharmharcanna.\n"
"Má chumasaíonn tú an rogha seo, cuirfear srian leis an taispeáint do theidil "
"chaibidle na mbarra dul chun cinn."

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1353
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1363
msgid "ToC entries per page"
msgstr "Iontrálacha Téarmaí Cinniúint in aghaidh an leathanaigh"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1376
#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1388
msgid "ToC entry font size"
msgstr "Méid cló iontrála ToC"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1397
msgid "Show chapter length"
msgstr "Taispeáin fad na caibidle"

#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertoc.lua:1408
msgid "Dot leaders"
msgstr "Ceannairí ponc"

