#: frontend/apps/reader/modules/readertypography.lua:132
msgid ""
"Some languages have specific typographic rules: these include hyphenation, "
"line breaking rules, and language specific glyph variants.\n"
"KOReader will choose one according to the language tag from the book's "
"metadata, but you can select another one.\n"
"You can also set a default language or a fallback one with a long-press.\n"
"\n"
"Features available per language are marked with:\n"
"‐ : language specific hyphenation dictionary\n"
" : specific line breaking rules (mostly related to quotation marks)\n"
" : more line breaking rules (e.g., single letter prepositions not allowed "
"at end of line)\n"
"\n"
"Note that when a language does not come with its own hyphenation dictionary, "
"the English (US) one will be used.\n"
"When the book's language tag is not among our presets, no specific features "
"will be enabled, but it might be enough to get language specific glyph "
"variants (when supported by the fonts)."
msgstr ""
"Tá rialacha clóghrafaíochta sonracha ag roinnt teangacha: áirítear leo seo "
"fleiscíní, rialacha briseadh líne, agus malairtí glif atá sainiúil don "
"teanga.\n"
"Roghnóidh KOReader ceann amháin de réir an chlib teanga ó mheiteashonraí an "
"leabhair, ach is féidir leat ceann eile a roghnú.\n"
"Is féidir leat teanga réamhshocraithe nó teanga chúltaca a shocrú freisin le "
"brú fada.\n"
"\n"
"Tá gnéithe atá ar fáil in aghaidh na teanga marcáilte le:\n"
": foclóir fleiscíní atá sainiúil don teanga\n"
": rialacha briseadh líne sonracha (a bhaineann den chuid is mó le "
"comharthaí athfhriotail)\n"
": tuilleadh rialacha briseadh líne (m.sh., ní cheadaítear réamhfhocail "
"aonlitir ag deireadh na líne)\n"
"\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara nuair nach bhfuil foclóir fleiscíní féin ag teanga, go n-"
"úsáidfear an ceann Béarla (SAM).\n"
"Nuair nach bhfuil clib teanga an leabhair i measc ár réamhshocruithe, ní "
"chuirfear aon ghnéithe sonracha ar siúl, ach d'fhéadfadh sé a bheith "
"leordhóthanach chun malairtí glif atá sainiúil don teanga a fháil (nuair a "
"thacaíonn na clónna leis)."

