#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:125
msgid ""
"Render the document on half the screen width and display two pages at once "
"with a single page number. This makes it look like two columns.\n"
"This is disabled in scroll mode. Switching from page mode with two columns "
"to scroll mode will cause the document to be re-rendered."
msgstr ""
"Rindreáil an doiciméad ar leath leithead an scáileáin agus taispeáin dhá "
"leathanach ag an am céanna le huimhir leathanaigh amháin. Fágann sé seo go "
"bhfuil cuma dhá cholún air.\n"
"Tá sé seo díchumasaithe i mód scrollaithe. Má athraítear ó mhodh leathanaigh "
"le dhá cholún go mód scrollaithe, déanfar an doiciméad a athrindreáil."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:135
msgid "L/R Margins"
msgstr "Imeall C/D"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:166
msgid "Left/Right Margins"
msgstr "Imeall Clé/Deas"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:180
msgid "Sync T/B Margins"
msgstr "Sioncrónaigh Corrlaigh T/B"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:181
msgctxt "Sync T/B margins"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:181
msgctxt "Sync T/B margins"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:188
msgid ""
"Keep top and bottom margins synchronized.\n"
"- 'off' allows different top and bottom margins.\n"
"- 'on' keeps top and bottom margins locked, ensuring text is vertically "
"centered in the page.\n"
"\n"
"In the top menu → Settings → Status bar, you can choose whether the bottom "
"margin applies from the bottom of the screen, or from above the status bar."
msgstr ""
"Coinnigh na corrlaigh uachtaracha agus íochtaracha sioncrónaithe.\n"
"- ceadaíonn 'as' corrlaigh uachtaracha agus íochtaracha difriúla.\n"
"- coinníonn 'ar' corrlaigh uachtaracha agus íochtaracha faoi ghlas, ag "
"cinntiú go bhfuil an téacs lárnaithe go hingearach sa leathanach.\n"
"\n"
"Sa roghchlár uachtarach → Socruithe → Barra stádais, is féidir leat a roghnú "
"an bhfuil an corrlach íochtarach i bhfeidhm ó bhun an scáileáin, nó ó os "
"cionn an bharra stádais."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:196
msgid "Top Margin"
msgstr "Corrlach Barr"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:231 frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:283
msgid "Top/Bottom Margins"
msgstr "Imill Uachtair/Bun"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:249
msgid "Bottom Margin"
msgstr "Imeall Bun"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:279
msgid ""
"In the top menu → Settings → Status bar, you can choose whether the bottom "
"margin applies from the bottom of the screen, or from above the status bar."
msgstr ""
"Sa roghchlár barr → Socruithe → Barra stádais, is féidir leat a roghnú an "
"bhfuil an corrlach bun i bhfeidhm ó bhun an scáileáin, nó ó os cionn an "
"bharra stádais."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:306 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:344
msgid "View Mode"
msgstr "Mód Amhairc"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:307 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:345
msgctxt "View mode"
msgid "page"
msgstr "leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:307 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:345
msgctxt "View mode"
msgid "continuous"
msgstr "leanúnach"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:313
msgid ""
"- 'page' mode splits the text into pages, at the most acceptable places "
"(page numbers and the number of pages may change when you change fonts, "
"margins, styles, etc.).\n"
"- 'continuous' mode allows you to scroll the text like you would in a web "
"browser (the 'Page Overlap' setting is only available in this mode)."
msgstr ""
"- roinneann mód 'leathanaigh' an téacs ina leathanaigh, sna háiteanna is "
"inghlactha (féadfaidh uimhreacha leathanach agus líon na leathanach athrú "
"nuair a athraíonn tú clónna, corrlaigh, stíleanna, srl.).\n"
"- ligeann mód 'leanúnach' duit an téacs a scrollú mar a dhéanfá i "
"mbrabhsálaí gréasáin (níl an socrú 'Forluí Leathanach' ar fáil ach sa mhodh "
"seo)."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:318
msgid "Render Mode"
msgstr "Mód Rindreála"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:319
msgctxt "Render mode"
msgid "legacy"
msgstr "oidhreacht"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:319
msgctxt "Render mode"
msgid "flat"
msgstr "cothrom"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:319
msgctxt "Render mode"
msgid "book"
msgstr "leabhar"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:319
msgctxt "Render mode"
msgid "web"
msgstr "gréasán"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:325
msgid ""
"- 'legacy' uses original CR3 block rendering code.\n"
"- 'flat' ensures flat rendering with collapsing margins and accurate page "
"breaks.\n"
"- 'book' additionally allows floats, but limits style support to avoid blank "
"spaces and overflows.\n"
"- 'web' renders as web browsers do, allowing negative margins and possible "
"page overflow."
msgstr ""
"- úsáideann 'legacy' cód rindreála bloic CR3 bunaidh.\n"
"- cinntíonn 'flat' rindreáil chomhréidh le corrlaigh atá ag dul i laghad "
"agus briseadh leathanaigh cruinne.\n"
"- ceadaíonn 'book' snámháin freisin, ach cuireann sé teorainn le tacaíocht "
"stíl chun spásanna bána agus ró-shreabhadh a sheachaint.\n"
"- rindreálann 'web' mar a dhéanann brabhsálaithe gréasáin, rud a cheadaíonn "
"corrlaigh dhiúltacha agus ró-shreabhadh leathanaigh féideartha."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:333
msgid "Zoom (dpi)"
msgstr "Zúmáil (dpi)"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:337
msgctxt "Resolution"
msgid "dpi"
msgstr "dpi"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:339
msgctxt "Zoom dpi"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:344
msgid ""
"Sets the DPI used to scale absolute CSS units and images:\n"
"- off: ignore absolute units (old engine behavior).\n"
"- 96¹’¹: at 96 DPI, 1 CSS pixel = 1 screen pixel and images are rendered at "
"their original dimensions.\n"
"- other values scale CSS absolute units and images by a factor (300 DPI = "
"x3, 48 DPI = x0.5)\n"
"Using your device's actual DPI will ensure 1 cm in CSS actually translates "
"to 1 cm on screen.\n"
"Note that your selected font size is not affected by this setting."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn sé an DPI a úsáidtear chun aonaid agus íomhánna absalóideacha CSS "
"a scálú:\n"
"- as: neamhaird a dhéanamh d'aonaid absalóideacha (iompar sean-innill).\n"
"- 96¹’¹: ag 96 DPI, 1 picteilín CSS = 1 picteilín scáileáin agus "
"rindreáiltear íomhánna ag a dtoisí bunaidh.\n"
"- luachanna eile scálaíonn aonaid agus íomhánna absalóideacha CSS de réir "
"fachtóra (300 DPI = x3, 48 DPI = x0.5)\n"
"Má úsáideann tú DPI iarbhír do ghléis, cinnteoidh sé go n-aistrítear 1 cm i "
"CSS go 1 cm ar an scáileán i ndáiríre.\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara nach ndéanann an socrú seo difear do mhéid cló roghnaithe."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:362 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:378
msgid "Line Spacing"
msgstr "Spásáil Líne"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:430 frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:431
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:440 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:441
msgctxt "Font size"
msgid "decrease"
msgstr "laghdú"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:430 frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:431
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:440 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:441
msgctxt "Font size"
msgid "increase"
msgstr "méadú"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:458
msgid "Word Spacing"
msgstr "Spásáil Focal"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:462
msgid "Word spacing"
msgstr "Spásáil focal"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:463
msgid ""
"Set word spacing percentages:\n"
"- how much to scale the width of each space character from its regular "
"width,\n"
"- by how much some of them can then be reduced to make more words fit on a "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh céatadáin spásála focal:\n"
"- cé mhéad le scálú leithead gach carachtair spáis óna leithead rialta,\n"
"- cé mhéad is féidir cuid acu a laghdú ansin chun níos mó focal a fheistiú "
"ar líne."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:466
msgid "Scaling"
msgstr "Scálú"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:471
msgid "Reduction"
msgstr "Laghdú"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:479
msgctxt "Word spacing"
msgid "small"
msgstr "beag"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:479
msgctxt "Word spacing"
msgid "medium"
msgstr "meánach"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:479
msgctxt "Word spacing"
msgid "large"
msgstr "mór"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:492
msgid ""
"Tells the rendering engine by how much to scale the width of each 'space' "
"character in the text from its regular width, and by how much it can "
"additionally reduce them to make more words fit on a line (100% means no "
"reduction)."
msgstr ""
"Insíonn sé don inneall rindreála cé mhéad atá le scálú leithead gach "
"carachtair 'spáis' sa téacs óna leithead rialta, agus cé mhéad is féidir "
"leis iad a laghdú freisin chun níos mó focal a fheistiú ar líne (ciallaíonn "
"100% gan aon laghdú)."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:501
msgid "Word Expansion"
msgstr "Leathnú Focal"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:510
msgid "Max word expansion"
msgstr "Uasmhéid leathnú focal"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:511
msgid "Set max word expansion as a percentage of the font size."
msgstr "Socraigh uasmhéid leathnú focal mar chéatadán den mhéid cló."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:514
msgid "CJK scaling"
msgstr "Scálú CJK"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:518
msgctxt "Word expansion"
msgid "none"
msgstr "aon cheann"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:518
msgctxt "Word expansion"
msgid "some"
msgstr "roinnt"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:518
msgctxt "Word expansion"
msgid "more"
msgstr "níos mó"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:531
msgid ""
"On justified lines having too wide spaces, allow distributing the excessive "
"space into words by expanding them with letter spacing. This sets the max "
"allowed letter spacing as a % of the font size."
msgstr ""
"Ar línte comhfhírinnithe a bhfuil spásanna ró-leathan iontu, ceadaigh an "
"spás iomarcach a dháileadh i bhfocail trína leathnú le spásáil litreacha. "
"Socraíonn sé seo an spásáil litreacha uasta a cheadaítear mar % den mhéid "
"cló."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:556
msgid "CJK width scaling"
msgstr "Scálú leithead CJK"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:557
msgid ""
"Increase the width of all CJK (Chinese, Japanese, Korean) characters by this "
"percentage. This has the effect of adding space between these glyphs, and "
"might make them easier to distinguish to some readers."
msgstr ""
"Méadaigh leithead na gcarachtar CJK (Sínis, Seapáinis, Cóiréis) go léir "
"faoin gcéatadán seo. Cuireann sé seo spás leis na glifí seo, agus "
"d’fhéadfadh sé go mbeadh sé níos fusa iad a aithint do roinnt léitheoirí."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:560
msgid "Word expansion"
msgstr "Leathnú focal"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:572 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:490
msgid "Contrast"
msgstr "Codarsnacht"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:597
msgid "Font Weight"
msgstr "Meáchan Cló"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:611
msgid ""
"Set the font weight delta from \"regular\" to apply to all fonts.\n"
"\n"
"- 0 will use the \"Regular (400)\" variation of a font.\n"
"- +1 will use the \"Medium (500)\" variation of a font if available.\n"
"- +3 will use the \"Bold (700)\" variation of a font if available.\n"
"If a font variation is not available, as well as for fractional adjustments, "
"it will be synthesized from the nearest available weight."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh delta meáchain an chló ó \"rialta\" le cur i bhfeidhm ar gach cló.\n"
"\n"
"- Úsáidfidh 0 an leagan \"Rialta (400)\" de chló.\n"
"- Úsáidfidh +1 an leagan \"Meánach (500)\" de chló más ann dó.\n"
"- Úsáidfidh +3 an leagan \"Trom (700)\" de chló más ann dó.\n"
"Mura bhfuil leagan cló ar fáil, chomh maith le haghaidh coigeartuithe "
"codánacha, déanfar é a shintéisiú ón meáchan is gaire atá ar fáil."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:621
msgid "The default font '%1' provides the following weight classes: %2."
msgstr ""
"Soláthraíonn an cló réamhshocraithe '%1' na haicmí meáchain seo a leanas: %2."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:621
msgctxt "List separator"
msgid ", "
msgstr ", "

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:631
msgid "Font Hinting"
msgstr "Leid Cló"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:632
msgctxt "Font hinting"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:632
msgctxt "Font hinting"
msgid "native"
msgstr "dúchasach"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:632
msgctxt "Font hinting"
msgid "auto"
msgstr "uath"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:638
msgid ""
"Font hinting is the process by which fonts are adjusted for maximum "
"readability on the screen's pixel grid.\n"
"\n"
"- off: no hinting.\n"
"- native: use the font internal hinting instructions.\n"
"- auto: use FreeType's hinting algorithm, ignoring font instructions."
msgstr ""
"Is éard atá i gceist le leid clónna ná an próiseas trína ndéantar clónna a "
"choigeartú le haghaidh inléiteachta uasta ar eangach picteilín an "
"scáileáin.\n"
"\n"
"- múchta: gan leid.\n"
"- dúchasach: bain úsáid as treoracha leid inmheánacha an chló.\n"
"- uathoibríoch: bain úsáid as algartam leid FreeType, ag neamhaird a "
"dhéanamh de threoracha clónna."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:646
msgid "Font Kerning"
msgstr "Cló-chorrú"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:647
msgctxt "Font kerning"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:647
msgctxt "Font kerning"
msgid "fast"
msgstr "tapa"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:647
msgctxt "Font kerning"
msgid "good"
msgstr "maith"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:647
msgctxt "Font kerning"
msgid "best"
msgstr "is fearr"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:653
msgid ""
"Font kerning is the process of adjusting the spacing between individual "
"letter forms, to achieve a visually pleasing result.\n"
"\n"
"- off: no kerning.\n"
"- fast: use FreeType's kerning implementation (no ligatures).\n"
"- good: use HarfBuzz's light kerning implementation (faster than best but no "
"ligatures and limited support for non-western scripts)\n"
"- best: use HarfBuzz's full kerning implementation (slower, but may support "
"ligatures with some fonts; also needed to properly display joined arabic "
"glyphs and some other scripts).\n"
"\n"
"(Font Hinting may need to be adjusted for the best result with either "
"kerning implementation.)"
msgstr ""
"Is éard is cornú cló ann ná próiseas chun an spásáil idir foirmeacha "
"litreacha aonair a choigeartú, chun toradh taitneamhach ó thaobh amhairc de "
"a bhaint amach.\n"
"\n"
"- as: gan cornú.\n"
"- tapa: bain úsáid as cur i bhfeidhm cornú FreeType (gan ligatúir).\n"
"- maith: bain úsáid as cur i bhfeidhm cornú éadrom HarfBuzz (níos tapúla ná "
"an ceann is fearr ach gan ligatúir agus tacaíocht theoranta do scripteanna "
"neamh-iartharacha)\n"
"- an ceann is fearr: bain úsáid as cur i bhfeidhm cornú iomlán HarfBuzz "
"(níos moille, ach d'fhéadfadh sé tacú le ligatúir le roinnt clónna; tá sé "
"riachtanach freisin chun glifí Araibis ceangailte agus roinnt scripteanna "
"eile a thaispeáint i gceart).\n"
"\n"
"(B'fhéidir go mbeadh gá le Leideanna Cló a choigeartú chun an toradh is "
"fearr a fháil le ceachtar cur i bhfeidhm cornú.)"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:669
msgid "Alt Status Bar"
msgstr "Barra Stádais Alt"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:670
msgctxt "Alt status bar"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:670
msgctxt "Alt status bar"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:676
msgid ""
"Enable or disable the rendering engine alternative status bar at the top of "
"the screen. The items displayed can be customized via the main menu.\n"
"\n"
"Whether enabled or disabled, KOReader's own status bar at the bottom of the "
"screen can be toggled by tapping."
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh nó díchumasaigh barra stádais malartach an innill rindreála ag "
"barr an scáileáin. Is féidir na míreanna a thaispeántar a shaincheapadh tríd "
"an bpríomh-roghchlár.\n"
"\n"
"Cibé acu cumasaithe nó díchumasaithe atá sé, is féidir barra stádais "
"KOReader féin ag bun an scáileáin a athrú trí thapáil."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:682
msgid "Embedded Style"
msgstr "Stíl Leabaithe"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:683
msgctxt "Embedded style"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:683
msgctxt "Embedded style"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:689
msgid ""
"Enable or disable publisher stylesheets embedded in the book.\n"
"(Note that less radical changes can be achieved via Style Tweaks in the main "
"menu.)"
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh nó díchumasaigh stílbileoga foilsitheora atá leabaithe sa "
"leabhar.\n"
"(Tabhair faoi deara gur féidir athruithe nach bhfuil chomh radacach a bhaint "
"amach trí Style Tweaks sa phríomh-roghchlár.)"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:694
msgid "Embedded Fonts"
msgstr "Clónna Leabaithe"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:695
msgctxt "Embedded fonts"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:695
msgctxt "Embedded fonts"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:705
msgid ""
"Enable or disable the use of the fonts embedded in the book.\n"
"(Disabling the fonts specified in the publisher stylesheets can also be "
"achieved via Style Tweaks in the main menu.)"
msgstr ""
"Cumasaigh nó díchumasaigh úsáid na gclónna atá leabaithe sa leabhar.\n"
"(Is féidir na clónna atá sonraithe i stílbhileoga an fhoilsitheora a "
"dhíchumasú trí Style Tweaks sa phríomh-roghchlár freisin.)"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:711
msgid "Embedded fonts provided by the current book:"
msgstr "Clónna leabaithe arna soláthar ag an leabhar reatha:"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:713
msgid "not used"
msgstr "nach n-úsáidtear"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:721
msgid "Image Scaling"
msgstr "Scálú Íomhá"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:722
msgctxt "Image scaling"
msgid "fast"
msgstr "tapa"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:722
msgctxt "Image scaling"
msgid "best"
msgstr "is fearr"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:728
msgid ""
"- 'fast' uses a fast but inaccurate scaling algorithm when scaling images.\n"
"- 'best' switches to a more costly but vastly more pleasing and accurate "
"algorithm."
msgstr ""
"- úsáideann 'fast' algartam scálúcháin tapa ach míchruinn agus íomhánna á "
"scálú.\n"
"- aistríonn 'best' go halgartam níos costasaí ach i bhfad níos taitneamhaí "
"agus níos cruinne."

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:733
msgid "Invert Images"
msgstr "Inbhéartaigh Íomhánna"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:734
msgctxt "Invert images"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:734
msgctxt "Invert images"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/creoptions.lua:741
msgid ""
"Disable the automagic inversion of images when nightmode is enabled. Useful "
"if your book contains mainly inlined mathematical content or scene break art."
msgstr ""
"Díchumasaigh inbhéartú uathoibríoch draíochta íomhánna nuair a bhíonn mód "
"oíche cumasaithe. Úsáideach má tá ábhar matamaiticiúil inlíneáilte nó ealaín "
"briseadh radhairc den chuid is mó i do leabhar."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:34
msgctxt "Style tweaks category"
msgid "Pages and margins"
msgstr "Leathanaigh agus corrlaigh"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:37
msgid "Ignore publisher page margins"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de imeall leathanaigh an fhoilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:38
msgid ""
"Force page margins to be 0, and may allow KOReader's margin settings to work "
"on books where they would not."
msgstr ""
"Éilíonn sé corrlaigh leathanaigh go 0, agus d’fhéadfadh sé go gceadófaí do "
"shocruithe corrlaigh KOReader oibriú ar leabhair nach n-oibreodh siad orthu."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:42
msgid "Horizontal margins"
msgstr "Imeall cothrománach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:46
msgid "Ignore all horizontal margins"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de na corrlaigh chothrománacha go léir"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:52
msgid "Ignore all horizontal padding"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird ar an líonadh cothrománach go léir"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:59
msgid "Ignore horizontal paragraph margins"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de imeall cothrománach mír"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:65
msgid "Ignore horizontal paragraph padding"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird den líonadh cothrománach míre"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:70
msgid "Vertical margins"
msgstr "Imeall ingearach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:74
msgid "Ignore all vertical margins"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de na corrlaigh ingearacha go léir"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:80
msgid "Ignore all vertical padding"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird ar an líonadh ingearach go léir"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:87
msgid "Ignore vertical paragraph margins"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de imeall mír ingearach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:93
msgid "Ignore vertical paragraph padding"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de líonadh ingearach na míre"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:99
msgid "Page breaks and blank pages"
msgstr "Briseadh leathanaigh agus leathanaigh bhána"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:102
msgid "Avoid blank page on chapter start"
msgstr "Seachain leathanach bán ag tús na caibidle"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:109
msgid "Avoid blank page on chapter end"
msgstr "Seachain leathanach bán ag deireadh na caibidle"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:115
msgid "Avoid publisher page breaks"
msgstr "Seachain briseadh leathanaigh an fhoilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:116
msgid ""
"Disable all publisher page breaks, keeping only KOReader's epub.css ones.\n"
"When combined with the two previous tweaks, all page-breaks are disabled."
msgstr ""
"Díchumasaigh gach briseadh leathanaigh de chuid an fhoilsitheora, ag "
"coinneáil cinn epub.css KOReader amháin.\n"
"Nuair a chuirtear leis an dá choigeartú roimhe seo iad, díchumasaítear gach "
"briseadh leathanaigh."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:128
msgid "New page on headings"
msgstr "Leathanach nua ar cheannteidil"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:131
msgid "New page on <H1>"
msgstr "Leathanach nua ar <H1>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:136
msgid "New page on <H2>"
msgstr "Leathanach nua ar <H2>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:144
msgid "New page on <H3>"
msgstr "Leathanach nua ar <H3>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:152
msgid "New page on <H4>"
msgstr "Leathanach nua ar <H4>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:160
msgid "New page on <H5>"
msgstr "Leathanach nua ar <H5>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:168
msgid "New page on <H6>"
msgstr "Leathanach nua ar <H6>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:177
msgid "Widows and orphans"
msgstr "Baintreacha agus dílleachtaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:179
msgid "About widow and orphan lines"
msgstr "Maidir le línte baintreacha agus dílleachtaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:180
msgid ""
"Widows and orphans are lines at the beginning or end of a paragraph, which "
"are left dangling at the top or bottom of a page, separated from the rest of "
"the paragraph.\n"
"The first line of a paragraph alone at the bottom of a page is called an "
"orphan line.\n"
"The last line of a paragraph alone at the top of a page is called a widow "
"line.\n"
"\n"
"Some people (and publishers) don't like widows and orphans, and can avoid "
"them with CSS rules.\n"
"To avoid widows and orphans, some lines have to be pushed to the next page "
"to accompany what would otherwise be widows and orphans. This may leave some "
"blank space at the bottom of the previous page, which might be more "
"disturbing to others.\n"
"\n"
"The default is to allow widows and orphans.\n"
"These tweaks allow you to change this behavior, and to override publisher "
"rules."
msgstr ""
"Is línte iad baintreacha agus dílleachtaí ag tús nó ag deireadh míre, a "
"fhágtar crochta ag barr nó ag bun leathanaigh, scartha ón gcuid eile den "
"mhír.\n"
"Tugtar líne dhílleachtaí ar an gcéad líne de mhír ina haonar ag bun "
"leathanaigh.\n"
"Tugtar líne baintreacha ar an líne dheireanach de mhír ina haonar ag barr "
"leathanaigh.\n"
"\n"
"Ní maith le roinnt daoine (agus foilsitheoirí) baintreacha agus dílleachtaí, "
"agus is féidir leo iad a sheachaint le rialacha CSS.\n"
"Chun baintreacha agus dílleachtaí a sheachaint, caithfear roinnt línte a "
"bhrú go dtí an chéad leathanach eile chun dul leis an méid a bheadh ina "
"mbaintreacha agus ina ndílleachtaí murach sin. D’fhéadfadh sé seo roinnt "
"spáis bhán a fhágáil ag bun an leathanaigh roimhe sin, rud a d’fhéadfadh a "
"bheith níos suaite do dhaoine eile.\n"
"\n"
"Is é an réamhshocrú ná baintreacha agus dílleachtaí a cheadú.\n"
"Ligeann na tweaks seo duit an t-iompar seo a athrú, agus rialacha "
"foilsitheora a shárú."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:201
msgid "Avoid widows and orphans"
msgstr "Seachain baintreacha agus dílleachtaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:202
msgid ""
"Avoid widow and orphan lines, allowing for some possible blank space at the "
"bottom of pages."
msgstr ""
"Seachain línte baintreacha agus dílleachtaí, agus fág roinnt spáis bhán ag "
"bun na leathanach."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:215
msgid "Avoid widows but allow orphans"
msgstr "Seachain baintreacha ach lig do dhílleachtaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:216
msgid ""
"Avoid widow lines, but allow orphan lines, allowing for some possible blank "
"space at the bottom of pages.\n"
"Allowing orphans avoids ambiguous blank space at the bottom of a page, which "
"could otherwise be confused with real spacing between paragraphs."
msgstr ""
"Seachain línte baintreacha, ach lig línte dílleachta, ag ligean roinnt spáis "
"bhán ag bun na leathanach.\n"
"Trí dhílleachta a cheadú, seachnaítear spás bán débhríoch ag bun "
"leathanaigh, a d’fhéadfaí a mheascadh le spásáil iarbhír idir míreanna "
"murach sin."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:231
msgid "Ignore publisher orphan and widow rules"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de rialacha dílleachta agus baintreacha foilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:232
msgid "Disable orphan and widow rules specified in embedded styles."
msgstr ""
"Díchumasaigh rialacha dílleachta agus baintreacha atá sonraithe i stíleanna "
"leabaithe."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:243
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Téacs"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:245
msgid "Text alignment"
msgstr "Ailíniú téacs"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:249
msgid "Left align most text"
msgstr "Ailínigh an chuid is mó den téacs ar chlé"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:250
msgid "Enforce left alignment of text in common text elements."
msgstr "Cuir ailíniú clé téacs i bhfeidhm in eilimintí téacs coitianta."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:257
msgid "Left align all elements"
msgstr "Ailínigh na heilimintí go léir ar chlé"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:258
msgid "Enforce left alignment of text in all elements."
msgstr "Cuir ailíniú clé téacs i bhfeidhm i ngach eilimint."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:266
msgid "Justify most text"
msgstr "Comhfhírinnigh an chuid is mó den téacs"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:267
msgid ""
"Text justification is the default, but it may be overridden by publisher "
"styles. This will re-enable it for most common text elements."
msgstr ""
"Is é údarú téacs an rogha réamhshocraithe, ach féadfaidh stíleanna "
"foilsitheora é a shárú. Athchumasóidh sé seo é don chuid is mó de na "
"heilimintí téacs coitianta."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:280
msgid "Justify all elements"
msgstr "Tabhair údar do na heilimintí uile"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:281
msgid ""
"Text justification is the default, but it may be overridden by publisher "
"styles. This will force justification on all elements, some of which may not "
"be centered as expected."
msgstr ""
"Is é an údarú téacs an rogha réamhshocraithe, ach féadfaidh stíleanna "
"foilsitheora é a shárú. Cuirfidh sé seo údarú i bhfeidhm ar gach eilimint, "
"agus ní fhéadfadh cuid acu a bheith lárnaithe mar a bhíothas ag súil leis."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:293
msgid "Center headings"
msgstr "Ceannteidil lárnaithe"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:299
msgid "Text direction"
msgstr "Treo an téacs"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:301
msgid "About text direction"
msgstr "Maidir le treo an téacs"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:302
msgid ""
"Languages like Arabic or Hebrew use right-to-left writing systems (Right-To-"
"Left or RTL). This doesn't only affect text layout, but also list item "
"bullets and numbers, which have to be put on the right side of the page, as "
"well as tables, where the cells are laid out from right to left.\n"
"\n"
"Usually, the publisher will have set the appropriate tags to enable RTL "
"rendering. But if these are missing, or if you're reading plain text "
"documents, you may want to manually enable RTL with these tweaks.\n"
"Note that in the absence of such specifications, KOReader will try to detect "
"the language of each paragraph to set the appropriate rendering per "
"paragraph.\n"
"\n"
"You may also want to enable, in the top menu → Gear → Taps and gestures → "
"Page turns → Invert page turn taps and swipes."
msgstr ""
"Úsáideann teangacha cosúil leis an Araibis nó an Eabhrais córais "
"scríbhneoireachta deas-go-clé (Deas-go-Clé nó RTL). Ní hamháin go mbíonn "
"tionchar aige seo ar leagan amach an téacs, ach freisin ar urchair agus "
"uimhreacha míreanna liosta, a chaithfear a chur ar thaobh na láimhe deise "
"den leathanach, chomh maith le táblaí, áit a leagtar amach na cealla ó dheas "
"go clé.\n"
"\n"
"De ghnáth, beidh na clibeanna cuí socraithe ag an bhfoilsitheoir chun "
"rindreáil RTL a chumasú. Ach mura bhfuil siad seo ann, nó má tá tú ag léamh "
"cáipéisí téacs simplí, b'fhéidir gur mhaith leat RTL a chumasú de láimh leis "
"na coigeartuithe seo.\n"
"Tabhair faoi deara, in éagmais na sonraíochtaí sin, go ndéanfaidh KOReader "
"iarracht teanga gach míre a bhrath chun an rindreáil chuí a shocrú in "
"aghaidh na míre.\n"
"\n"
"B'fhéidir gur mhaith leat sconnaí agus svaidhpeálacha casadh leathanaigh a "
"chumasú freisin, sa roghchlár barr → Giar → Tapálacha agus gothaí → Casadh "
"leathanaigh → Inbhéartaigh tapálacha agus svaidhpeálacha casadh leathanaigh."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:314
msgid "Document direction RTL"
msgstr "Treo an doiciméid RTL"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:321
msgid "Right align most text"
msgstr "Ailínigh an chuid is mó den téacs ar dheis"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:322
msgid "Enforce right alignment of text in common text elements."
msgstr "Forfheidhmigh ailíniú ar dheis téacs in eilimintí téacs coitianta."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:330
msgid "Right align all elements"
msgstr "Ailínigh na heilimintí go léir ar dheis"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:331
msgid "Enforce right alignment of text in all elements."
msgstr "Cuir ailíniú ar dheis téacs i bhfeidhm i ngach eilimint."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:339
msgid "Document direction LTR"
msgstr "Treo an doiciméid LTR"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:345
msgid "Hyphenation, ligatures, ruby"
msgstr "Fleiscín, ligatúir, ruby"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:348
msgid "Allow hyphenation on all text"
msgstr "Ceadaigh fleiscín ar an téacs go léir"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:349
msgid ""
"Allow hyphenation on all text (except headings), in case the publisher has "
"disabled it."
msgstr ""
"Ceadaigh fleiscín a úsáid ar gach téacs (seachas ceannteidil), i gcás go "
"bhfuil sé díchumasaithe ag an bhfoilsitheoir."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:357
msgid "Ignore publisher line-break restrictions"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de shrianta briseadh líne an fhoilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:358
msgid ""
"A publisher might use non-breaking spaces and hyphens to avoid line breaking "
"between some words, which is not always necessary and may have been added to "
"make reading easier. This can cause large word spacing on some lines.\n"
"Ignoring them will only use KOReader's own typography rules for line "
"breaking."
msgstr ""
"D’fhéadfadh foilsitheoir spásanna neamh-bhriste agus fleiscíní a úsáid chun "
"briseadh líne a sheachaint idir roinnt focal, rud nach mbíonn riachtanach i "
"gcónaí agus a d’fhéadfadh a bheith curtha leis chun léamh a dhéanamh níos "
"éasca. Is féidir leis seo spásáil mhór focal a chur faoi deara ar roinnt "
"línte.\n"
"Má dhéantar neamhaird orthu, ní úsáidfear ach rialacha clóghrafaíochta "
"KOReader féin le haghaidh briseadh líne."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:365
msgid "Disable common ligatures"
msgstr "Díchumasaigh ligatúir choitianta"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:366
msgid ""
"Disable common ligatures, which are enabled by default in 'best' kerning "
"mode."
msgstr ""
"Díchumasaigh ligatúir choitianta, atá cumasaithe de réir réamhshocraithe sa "
"mhodh kernála 'is fearr'."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:375
msgid "Ruby"
msgstr "Ruby"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:377
msgid "About ruby"
msgstr "Maidir le ruby"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:378
msgid ""
"Ruby characters are small glosses on writing in Asian languages (Hanzi, "
"Kanji, Hanja, etc.) to show the pronunciation of the logographs.\n"
"These tweaks can help make ruby easier to read or ignore."
msgstr ""
"Is gearrchiorruithe beaga iad carachtair Ruby ar scríbhneoireacht i "
"dteangacha na hÁise (Hanzi, Kanji, Hanja, srl.) chun fuaimniú na logagraf a "
"thaispeáint.\n"
"Is féidir leis na hathruithe seo cabhrú le Ruby a dhéanamh níos éasca le "
"léamh nó neamhaird a dhéanamh air."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:385
msgid "Sans-serif font for ruby"
msgstr "Cló Sans-serif do Ruby"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:386
msgid ""
"Use a sans serif font to display all ruby text for a more 'book-like' "
"feeling.\n"
"Also force the regular text weight when used with lighter or bolder fonts."
msgstr ""
"Bain úsáid as cló sans serif chun an téacs go léir a thaispeáint le haghaidh "
"mothú níos 'leabhair'.\n"
"Cuir an meáchan téacs rialta i bhfeidhm freisin nuair a úsáidtear é le "
"clónna níos éadroime nó níos troma."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:398
msgid "Larger ruby text size"
msgstr "Méid téacs ruby níos mó"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:399
msgid "Increase ruby text size."
msgstr "Méadaigh méid téacs ruby."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:405
msgid "Larger spacing between ruby lines"
msgstr "Spásáil níos mó idir línte ruby"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:406
msgid ""
"Increase line spacing of most text, so that lines keep an even spacing "
"whether or not they include ruby.\n"
"Further small adjustments can be done with 'Line Spacing' in the bottom menu."
msgstr ""
"Méadaigh spásáil líne an chuid is mó den téacs, ionas go gcoinníonn línte "
"spásáil chothrom cibé acu atá ruby iontu nó nach bhfuil.\n"
"Is féidir coigeartuithe beaga breise a dhéanamh le 'Spásáil Líne' sa "
"roghchlár bun."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:414
msgid "Render ruby content inline"
msgstr "Rindreáil ábhar ruby inlíne"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:415
msgid "Disable handling of <ruby> tags and render them inline."
msgstr "Díchumasaigh láimhseáil clibeanna <ruby> agus rindreáil iad inlíne."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:422
msgid "Font size and families"
msgstr "Méid cló agus teaghlaigh"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:425
msgid "Ignore font related HTML presentational hints"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de leideanna cur i láthair HTML a bhaineann le clónna"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:426
msgid ""
"Ignore HTML attributes that contribute to styles on the elements <body> "
"(bgcolor, text…) and <font> (face, size, color…)."
msgstr ""
"Déan neamhaird de thréithe HTML a chuireann le stíleanna ar na heilimintí "
"<body> (bgcolor, text…) agus <font> (face, size, color…)."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:432
msgid "Ignore publisher font families"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de theaghlaigh clónna foilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:433
msgid "Disable font-family specified in embedded styles."
msgstr "Díchumasaigh an teaghlach clónna atá sonraithe i stíleanna leabaithe."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:444
msgid "Ignore publisher font sizes"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de mhéideanna cló an fhoilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:445
msgid "Disable font-size specified in embedded styles."
msgstr "Díchumasaigh an méid cló atá sonraithe i stíleanna leabaithe."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:452
msgid "Reset main text font size"
msgstr "Athshocraigh méid cló an phríomhthéacs"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:453
msgid ""
"Disable font-size set on the main text (keeping possibly larger headings "
"untouched), so that KOReader's font size is used."
msgstr ""
"Díchumasaigh an méid cló atá socraithe ar an bpríomhthéacs (ag coinneáil "
"ceannteidil níos mó fós), ionas go n-úsáidfear méid cló KOReader."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:459
msgid "Line heights"
msgstr "Airde na líne"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:462
msgid "Ignore publisher line heights"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird ar airde línte an fhoilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:463
msgid ""
"Disable line-height specified in embedded styles, and may allow KOReader's "
"line spacing settings to work on books where they would not."
msgstr ""
"Díchumasaigh airde líne atá sonraithe i stíleanna leabaithe, agus "
"d’fhéadfadh sé go gceadófaí do shocruithe spásála líne KOReader oibriú ar "
"leabhair nach n-oibreodh siad orthu."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:468
msgid "Enforce steady line heights"
msgstr "Airde líne seasta a fhorfheidhmiú"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:469
msgid ""
"Prevent inline content like sub- and superscript from changing their "
"paragraph line height."
msgstr ""
"Cosc a chur ar ábhar inlíne cosúil le fo-scríbhinn agus for-scríbhinn ó "
"airde líne na míre a athrú."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:476
msgid "Smaller sub- and superscript"
msgstr "Fo- agus for-scríbhinn níos lú"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:477
msgid "Prevent sub- and superscript from affecting line-height."
msgstr ""
"Cosc a chur ar fho-scríbhinn agus ar fhor-scríbhinn tionchar a imirt ar "
"airde na líne."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:488
msgid "Override font-based normal line height"
msgstr "Sáraigh airde líne gnáthbhunaithe ar chló"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:494
msgid "Normal line height: %1"
msgstr "Airde gnáthlíne: %1"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:509
msgid "Paragraphs"
msgstr "Paragraif"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:512
msgid "Generic web browser paragraph style"
msgstr "Stíl mhír bhrabhsálaí gréasáin ghinearálta"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:513
msgid ""
"Display paragraphs as browsers do, in full-block style without indentation "
"or justification, discarding KOReader's book paragraph style.\n"
"This might be needed with some documents that expect this style as the "
"default, and only use CSS when it needs to diverge from this default."
msgstr ""
"Taispeáin míreanna mar a dhéanann brabhsálaithe, i stíl lánbhloc gan eangú "
"ná údarú, ag fáil réidh le stíl mhír leabhair KOReader.\n"
"D’fhéadfadh sé seo a bheith riachtanach le roinnt doiciméad a bhfuiltear ag "
"súil leis an stíl seo mar an réamhshocrú, agus nach n-úsáideann CSS ach "
"amháin nuair is gá diall ón réamhshocrú seo."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:528
msgid "Tailor widths and text-indent for CJK"
msgstr "Leithead agus eangú téacs a oiriúnú do CJK"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:529
msgid ""
"Adjust paragraph width and text-indent to be an integer multiple of the font "
"size, so that lines of Chinese and Japanese characters don't need space "
"added between glyphs for text justification."
msgstr ""
"Coigeartaigh leithead na míre agus an t-eangú téacs ionas go mbeidh siad ina "
"ilchodach slánuimhir de mhéid an chló, ionas nach mbeidh gá spás a chur leis "
"idir glifí i línte de charachtair Síneacha agus Seapánacha chun téacs a "
"chomhlánú."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:535
msgid "Paragraph first-line indentation"
msgstr "Ionrú chéad líne na paragraf"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:538
msgid "No indentation on first paragraph line"
msgstr "Gan aon eangú ar an gcéad líne pharagraf"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:539
msgid "Do not indent the first line of paragraphs."
msgstr "Ná cuir an chéad líne de pharagraf isteach."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:545
msgid "Indentation on first paragraph line"
msgstr "Eangú ar an gcéad líne pharagraf"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:546
msgid ""
"Indentation on the first line of a paragraph is the default, but it may be "
"overridden by publisher styles. This will force KOReader's defaults on "
"common elements."
msgstr ""
"Is é an réamhshocrú ná an chéad líne de pharagraf a bheith ina heangach, ach "
"féadfaidh stíleanna foilsitheora é a shárú. Cuirfidh sé seo réamhshocruithe "
"KOReader i bhfeidhm ar eilimintí coitianta."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:554
msgid "No indentation on first paragraph"
msgstr "Gan aon eangú ar an gcéad paragraf"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:555
msgid ""
"Do not indent the first line of the first paragraph of its container. This "
"might be needed to correctly display drop caps, while still having "
"indentation on following paragraphs."
msgstr ""
"Ná cuir eangú ar an gcéad líne den chéad paragraf dá choimeádán. B’fhéidir "
"go mbeadh gá leis seo chun caipíní titim a thaispeáint i gceart, agus eangú "
"fós ar na paragraif ina dhiaidh sin."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:561
msgid "No indentation on following paragraphs"
msgstr "Gan aon eangú ar na paragraif seo a leanas"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:562
msgid ""
"Do not indent the first line of following paragraphs, but leave the first "
"paragraph of its container untouched."
msgstr ""
"Ná cuir isteach an chéad líne de na paragraif ina dhiaidh sin, ach fág an "
"chéad paragraf dá coimeádán gan teagmháil."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:568 frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:572
msgid "Spacing between paragraphs"
msgstr "Spásáil idir paragraif"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:573
msgid "Add a line of whitespace between paragraphs."
msgstr "Cuir líne spáis bhán idir paragraif."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:580
msgid "Spacing between paragraphs (half)"
msgstr "Spásáil idir paragraif (leath)"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:581
msgid "Add half a line of whitespace between paragraphs."
msgstr "Cuir leathlíne de spás bán idir paragraif."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:588
msgid "No spacing between paragraphs"
msgstr "Gan spásáil idir paragraif"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:589
msgid ""
"No whitespace between paragraphs is the default, but it may be overridden by "
"publisher styles. This will re-enable it for paragraphs and list items."
msgstr ""
"Is é an réamhshocrú nach mbíonn spás bán idir mhíreanna, ach féadfaidh "
"stíleanna foilsitheora é a shárú. Athchumasóidh sé seo é do pharagraif agus "
"do pharagraif liosta."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:596
msgid "Tables, links, images"
msgstr "Táblaí, naisc, íomhánna"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:598
msgid "Tables"
msgstr "Táblaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:601
msgid "Ignore tables related HTML presentational hints"
msgstr ""
"Déan neamhaird de na leideanna cur i láthair HTML a bhaineann le táblaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:602
msgid ""
"Ignore HTML attributes that contribute to styles on the <table> element and "
"its sub-elements (ie. align, valign, frame, rules, border, cellpadding, "
"cellspacing…)."
msgstr ""
"Déan neamhaird de thréithe HTML a chuireann le stíleanna ar an eilimint "
"<table> agus a fho-eilimintí (m.sh. ailíniú, bailíochtú, fráma, rialacha, "
"border, líonadh cealla, spásáil chealla…)."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:608
msgid "Full-width tables"
msgstr "Táblaí lánleithid"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:609
msgid ""
"Make table expand to the full width of the page. (Tables with small content "
"now use only the width needed to display that content. This restores the "
"previous behavior.)"
msgstr ""
"Leathnaigh an tábla go leithead iomlán an leathanaigh. (Ní úsáideann táblaí "
"a bhfuil ábhar beag acu ach an leithead atá riachtanach chun an t-ábhar sin "
"a thaispeáint anois. Athbhunaíonn sé seo an t-iompar roimhe seo.)"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:615
msgid "Ignore publisher table and cell widths"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de leithead tábla agus cille an fhoilsitheora"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:616
msgid ""
"Ignore table and cells widths specified by the publisher, and let the engine "
"decide the most appropriate widths."
msgstr ""
"Déan neamhaird de leithead táblaí agus cealla a shonraíonn an foilsitheoir, "
"agus lig don inneall cinneadh a dhéanamh ar na leithead is oiriúnaí."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:621
msgid "Center small tables"
msgstr "Táblaí beaga sa lár"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:622
msgid "Horizontally center tables that do not use the full page width."
msgstr ""
"Cuir táblaí nach n-úsáideann leithead iomlán an leathanaigh i lár go "
"cothrománach."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:629
msgid "Ignore publisher vertical alignment in tables"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de ailíniú ingearach an fhoilsitheora i dtáblaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:636
msgid "Alternate background color of table rows"
msgstr "Dath cúlra malartach sraitheanna tábla"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:644
msgid "Show borders on all tables"
msgstr "Taispeáin teorainneacha ar gach tábla"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:655
msgid "Links always black"
msgstr "Naisc i gcónaí dubh"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:661
msgid "Links always blue"
msgstr "Naisc gorm i gcónaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:668
msgid "Links always bold"
msgstr "Naisc i gcónaí i gcló trom"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:674
msgid "Links never bold"
msgstr "Naisc riamh i gcló trom"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:681
msgid "Links always italic"
msgstr "Naisc i gcló iodálach i gcónaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:687
msgid "Links never italic"
msgstr "Ní bhíonn naisc iodálach riamh"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:694
msgid "Links always underlined"
msgstr "Naisc faoi líne i gcónaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:701
msgid "Links never underlined"
msgstr "Ní bhíonn líne faoi naisc riamh"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:706
msgid "Images"
msgstr "Íomhánna"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:709
msgid "Full-width images"
msgstr "Íomhánna lánleithid"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:710
msgid ""
"Useful for books containing only images, when they are smaller than your "
"screen. May stretch images in some cases."
msgstr ""
"Úsáideach do leabhair ina bhfuil íomhánna amháin, nuair atá siad níos lú ná "
"do scáileán. Féadfaidh sé íomhánna a shíneadh i gcásanna áirithe."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:724
msgid "Vertically center-align images relative to text"
msgstr "Ailínigh íomhánna go hingearach i lár an téacs"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:730
msgid "Miscellaneous"
msgstr "Ilghnéitheach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:732
msgid "Alternative ToC hints"
msgstr "Leideanna malartacha maidir le Téarmaí Úsáide"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:734
msgid "About alternative ToC"
msgstr "Maidir le Téarmaí Úsáide Malartacha"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:735
msgid ""
"An alternative table of contents can be built via a dedicated option in the "
"\"Settings\" menu below the \"Table of contents\" menu entry.\n"
"\n"
"The ToC will be built from document headings <H1> to <H6>. Some of these can "
"be ignored with the tweaks available here.\n"
"If the document contains no headings, or all are ignored, the alternative "
"ToC will be built from document fragments and will point to the start of "
"each individual HTML file in the EPUB.\n"
"\n"
"Hints can be set to other non-heading elements in a user style tweak, so "
"they can be used as ToC items. Since this would be quite book-specific, "
"please see the final tweak for some examples.\n"
"\n"
"After applying these tweaks, the alternative ToC needs to be rebuilt by "
"toggling it twice in its menu: once to restore the original ToC, and once to "
"build the alternative ToC again."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir clár ábhair malartach a thógáil trí rogha tiomnaithe sa roghchlár "
"\"Socruithe\" faoin iontráil roghchláir \"Clár ábhair\".\n"
"\n"
"Tógfar an TOC ó cheannteidil doiciméad <H1> go <H6>. Is féidir neamhaird a "
"dhéanamh de chuid díobh seo leis na coigeartuithe atá ar fáil anseo.\n"
"Mura bhfuil aon cheannteidil sa doiciméad, nó má dhéantar neamhaird orthu "
"uile, tógfar an TOC malartach ó bhlúirí doiciméad agus pointeálfaidh sé tús "
"gach comhaid HTML aonair san EPUB.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leideanna a shocrú d'eilimintí eile nach ceannteidil iad i "
"gcoigeartú stíl úsáideora, ionas gur féidir iad a úsáid mar mhíreanna TOC. "
"Ós rud é go mbeadh sé seo sách sainiúil don leabhar, féach ar an gcoigeartú "
"deiridh le haghaidh roinnt samplaí.\n"
"\n"
"Tar éis na coigeartuithe seo a chur i bhfeidhm, ní mór an TOC malartach a "
"atógáil trína athrú faoi dhó ina roghchlár: uair amháin chun an TOC bunaidh "
"a athchóiriú, agus uair amháin chun an TOC malartach a thógáil arís."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:748
msgid "Ignore all <H1> to <H6>"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de gach rud <H1> go <H6>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:753
msgid "Ignore <H1>"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de <H1>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:758
msgid "Ignore <H2>"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de <H2>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:763
msgid "Ignore <H3>"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de <H3>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:768
msgid "Ignore <H4>"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de <H4>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:773
msgid "Ignore <H5>"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de <H5>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:778
msgid "Ignore <H6>"
msgstr "Déan neamhaird de <H6>"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:784
msgid "Example of book specific ToC hints"
msgstr "Sampla de leideanna maidir le Téarmaí Úsáide atá sainiúil don leabhar"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:785
msgid ""
"If headings or document fragments do not result in a usable ToC, you can "
"inspect the HTML and look for elements that contain chapter titles. Then you "
"can set hints to their class names.\n"
"This is just an example, that will need to be adapted into a user style "
"tweak."
msgstr ""
"Mura mbíonn ceannteidil nó blúirí doiciméad ina dtáirgeadh Téarmaí Úsáide "
"inúsáidte, is féidir leat an HTML a iniúchadh agus eilimintí ina bhfuil "
"teidil chaibidle a lorg. Ansin is féidir leat leideanna a shocrú dá n-"
"ainmneacha ranga.\n"
"Níl anseo ach sampla, a mbeidh gá é a oiriúnú i gcoigeartú stíl úsáideora."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:798
msgid "List items"
msgstr "Míreanna liosta"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:801
msgid "Force bullets with unordered lists"
msgstr "Fórsaigh urchair le liostaí neamhordaithe"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:806
msgid "Force decimal numbers with ordered lists"
msgstr "Fórsaigh uimhreacha deachúlacha le liostaí ordaithe"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:812
msgid "Disable before/after pseudo elements"
msgstr "Díchumasaigh eilimintí bréige roimh/i ndiaidh"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:813
msgid ""
"Disable generated text from ::before and ::after pseudo elements, usually "
"used to add cosmetic text around some content."
msgstr ""
"Díchumasaigh téacs ginte ó eilimintí bréige ::before agus ::after, a "
"úsáidtear de ghnáth chun téacs cosmaideach a chur timpeall ar roinnt ábhair."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:822
msgid "Pure black and white"
msgstr "Dubh agus bán íon"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:823
msgid "Enforce black text and borders, and remove backgrounds."
msgstr "Cuir téacs agus teorainneacha dubha i bhfeidhm, agus bain cúlraí."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:835
msgid "In-page footnotes"
msgstr "Nótaí coise sa leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:837 frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:840
msgid "In-page FB2 footnotes"
msgstr "Nótaí coise FB2 ar an leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:841
msgid ""
"Show FB2 footnote text at the bottom of pages that contain links to them."
msgstr "Taispeáin téacs nótaí FB2 ag bun na leathanach ina bhfuil naisc chucu."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:866
msgid "In-page FB2 endnotes"
msgstr "Nótaí deiridh FB2 ar an leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:867
msgid ""
"Show FB2 endnote text at the bottom of pages that contain links to them."
msgstr ""
"Taispeáin téacs nótaí deiridh FB2 ag bun na leathanach ina bhfuil naisc "
"chucu."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:889
msgid "Keep regular font size"
msgstr "Coinnigh méid cló rialta"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:890
msgid ""
"FB2 footnotes and endnotes get a smaller font size when displayed in-page. "
"This allows them to be shown with the normal font size."
msgstr ""
"Faigheann nótaí coise agus nótaí deiridh FB2 méid cló níos lú nuair a "
"thaispeántar iad sa leathanach. Fágann sé seo gur féidir iad a thaispeáint "
"leis an ngnáthmhéid cló."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:907
msgid "In-page EPUB footnotes"
msgstr "Nótaí coise EPUB sa leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:908
msgid ""
"Show EPUB footnote text at the bottom of pages that contain links to them.\n"
"This only works with footnotes that have specific attributes set by the "
"publisher."
msgstr ""
"Taispeáin téacs nótaí coise EPUB ag bun na leathanach ina bhfuil naisc "
"chucu.\n"
"Ní oibríonn sé seo ach le nótaí coise a bhfuil tréithe sonracha socraithe ag "
"an bhfoilsitheoir."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:932
msgid "In-page Wikipedia footnotes"
msgstr "Nótaí coise Vicipéide sa leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:933
msgid "Show footnotes at the bottom of pages in Wikipedia EPUBs."
msgstr "Taispeáin nótaí coise ag bun na leathanach in EPUBanna Vicipéide."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:952
msgid "In-page classic classname footnotes"
msgstr "Nótaí coise clasaiceacha ar an leathanach d’ainm ranga"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:953
msgid ""
"Show footnotes with classic classnames at the bottom of pages.\n"
"This tweak can be duplicated as a user style tweak when books contain "
"footnotes wrapped with other class names."
msgstr ""
"Taispeáin nótaí coise le hainmneacha clasaiceacha ranga ag bun na "
"leathanach.\n"
"Is féidir an coigeartú seo a dhúbailt mar choigeartú stíl úsáideora nuair a "
"bhíonn nótaí coise fillte le hainmneacha ranga eile i leabhair."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:973
msgid "In-page footnote extension"
msgstr "Síneadh nóta sa leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:977
msgid "Extend footnote content until next entry"
msgstr "Leathnaigh ábhar an fhonóta go dtí an chéad iontráil eile"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:978
msgid ""
"Extend in-page footnotes shown at the bottom of pages to include text up to "
"the next footnote.\n"
"This might be needed when books don't correctly mark all text that belongs "
"to the footnote."
msgstr ""
"Leathnaigh na nótaí coise sa leathanach a thaispeántar ag bun na leathanach "
"chun téacs a chur san áireamh suas go dtí an chéad nóta coise eile.\n"
"D’fhéadfadh sé seo a bheith riachtanach nuair nach ndéanann leabhair an "
"téacs go léir a bhaineann leis an nóta coise a mharcáil i gceart."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:996
msgid "Extend footnote content until next header"
msgstr "Leathnaigh ábhar an nóta go dtí an chéad cheanntásc eile"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:997
msgid ""
"Extend in-page footnotes shown at the bottom of pages to include text up to "
"the next footnote or heading.\n"
"This might be needed when books don't correctly mark all text that belongs "
"to the footnote.\n"
"This tweak can be duplicated as a user style tweak when a book contains "
"other elements between footnotes that should not be shown in-page."
msgstr ""
"Leathnaigh na nótaí coise sa leathanach a thaispeántar ag bun na leathanach "
"chun téacs a chur san áireamh suas go dtí an chéad nóta coise nó "
"ceannteideal eile.\n"
"D’fhéadfadh sé seo a bheith riachtanach nuair nach marcálann leabhair an "
"téacs go léir a bhaineann leis an nóta coise i gceart.\n"
"Is féidir an coigeartú seo a dhúbailt mar choigeartú stíl úsáideora nuair a "
"bhíonn eilimintí eile i leabhar idir nótaí coise nach ceart a thaispeáint sa "
"leathanach."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1027
msgid "In-page footnote font size"
msgstr "Méid cló an nóta coise sa leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1031
msgid "Smaller footnotes (80%, legacy)"
msgstr "Nótaí coise níos lú (80%, seanfhocail)"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1032
msgid ""
"Decrease size of in-page footnotes. This may have no effect if it's "
"overwritten by publisher styles. The \"footnote font size\" style tweaks are "
"recommended instead."
msgstr ""
"Laghdaigh méid na gcosnótaí sa leathanach. B’fhéidir nach mbeidh aon "
"éifeacht aige seo má scríobhann stíleanna foilsitheora tharstu. Moltar na "
"coigeartuithe stíl \"méid cló an chosnóta\" ina ionad."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1049
msgid "Footnote font size: %1 %"
msgstr "Méid cló nóta coise: %1 %"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1062
msgid "In-page footnote fix-up"
msgstr "Ceartú ar fhonóta sa leathanach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1065
msgid "No footnote indentation"
msgstr "Gan aon eangú san fhonóta"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1076
msgid "Justify footnote text"
msgstr "Comhfhírigh téacs an fhonóta"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1087
msgid "Remove block margins"
msgstr "Bain imeall bloc"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1088
msgid "Remove block margin and padding inside inpage footnotes."
msgstr ""
"Bain corrlach bloc agus líonadh taobh istigh de na nótaí coise inleathanaigh."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1101
msgid "Remove cosmetic spacing"
msgstr "Bain an spásáil chosmaideach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1102
msgid "Remove inline margin and padding inside inpage footnotes."
msgstr ""
"Bain an corrlach inlíne agus an líonadh taobh istigh de na nótaí coise "
"inleathanaigh."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1115
msgid "Inline all footnote content"
msgstr "Inlíne a chur ar gach ábhar nótaí"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1116
msgid ""
"If the footnote number is on a single line and the footnote text on the next "
"line, or if there are variable levels of indentation, this tweak can make "
"all the footnote content become a single paragraph.\n"
"This will break any complex footnote containing quotes or lists."
msgstr ""
"Más ar líne amháin atá uimhir an nóta coise agus téacs an nóta coise ar an "
"chéad líne eile, nó más ar leibhéil éagsúla eangaithe atá sé, is féidir leis "
"an gcoigeartú seo a dhéanamh go mbeidh ábhar an nóta coise ina mhír aonair.\n"
"Brisfidh sé seo aon nóta coise casta ina bhfuil luachana nó liostaí."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1137
msgid "Regularize text size on inline elements"
msgstr "Rialúigh méid an téacs ar eilimintí inlíne"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1138
msgid ""
"If the footnote text uses variable or absolute font sizes, line height or "
"vertical alignments, which would make it too irregular, you can reset all of "
"them to get a leaner text (to the expense of losing superscripts)."
msgstr ""
"Má úsáideann téacs an fhonóta méideanna cló athraitheacha nó absalóideacha, "
"airde líne nó ailínithe ingearacha, rud a fhágfadh ró-neamhrialta é, is "
"féidir leat iad go léir a athshocrú chun téacs níos tanaí a fháil (ar "
"chostas cailliúint forscríbhinní)."

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1153
msgid "Combine footnotes in a non-linear flow"
msgstr "Comhcheangail nótaí coise i sreabhadh neamhlíneach"

#: frontend/ui/data/css_tweaks.lua:1154
msgid ""
"This will mark each section of consecutive footnotes (at their original "
"location in the book) as being non-linear.\n"
"The menu checkbox \"Hide non-linear fragments\" will then be available after "
"the document is reopened, allowing to hide these sections from the regular "
"flow: they will be skipped when turning pages and not considered in the "
"various book & chapter progress and time to read features."
msgstr ""
"Marcálfaidh sé seo gach cuid de na nótaí coise as a chéile (ag a suíomh "
"bunaidh sa leabhar) mar chuid neamhlíneach.\n"
"Beidh an bosca seiceála roghchláir \"Folaigh blúirí neamhlíneacha\" ar fáil "
"ansin tar éis an doiciméad a athoscailt, rud a ligfidh duit na codanna seo a "
"cheilt ón ngnáthshreabhadh: scipeálfar iad agus leathanaigh á n-iompú agus "
"ní chuirfear san áireamh iad sna gnéithe éagsúla dul chun cinn leabhar & "
"caibidlí agus am le léamh."

