#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:334
msgid ""
"Set how paging and swiping forward should move the view on the page:\n"
"left to right or reverse, top to bottom or reverse."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh conas ba chóir go mbogfadh brabhsáil agus svaidhpeáil ar aghaidh an "
"radharc\n"
"ar an leathanach: ó chlé go deas nó ar gcúl, ó bharr go bun nó ar gcúl."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:351
msgid ""
"- 'page' mode shows only one page of the document at a time.\n"
"- 'continuous' mode allows you to scroll the pages like you would in a web "
"browser."
msgstr ""
"- ní thaispeánann mód 'leathanaigh' ach leathanach amháin den doiciméad ag "
"an am.\n"
"- sa mhodh 'leanúnach' is féidir leat scrollú trí na leathanaigh mar a "
"dhéanfá i mbrabhsálaí gréasáin."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:356
msgid "Page Gap"
msgstr "Bearna Leathanaigh"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:368
msgid ""
"In continuous view mode, sets the thickness of the separator between "
"document pages."
msgstr ""
"I mód radhairc leanúnaigh, socraítear tiús an deighilteora idir leathanaigh "
"an doiciméid."

