#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:412
msgctxt "Alignment"
msgid "justify"
msgstr "údar a thabhairt"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:415
msgid ""
"In reflow mode, sets the text alignment.\n"
"The first option (\"auto\") tries to automatically align reflowed text as it "
"is in the original document."
msgstr ""
"I mód athshreafa, socraítear ailíniú an téacs.\n"
"Déanann an chéad rogha (\"uathoibríoch\") iarracht téacs athshreafa a "
"ailíniú go huathoibríoch mar atá sé sa bhundhoiciméad."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:454
msgid ""
"In reflow mode, sets a font scaling factor that is applied to the original "
"document font sizes."
msgstr ""
"I mód athshreafa, socraítear fachtóir scálaithe cló a chuirtear i bhfeidhm "
"ar mhéideanna cló an doiciméid bhunaidh."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:461
