msgstr "I mód athshreafa, socraíonn sé an spásáil idir focail."

#. @translators Reflow text.
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:474
msgid "Reflow"
msgstr "Athshreabhadh"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:475
msgctxt "Reflow"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:475
msgctxt "Reflow"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:480
msgid ""
"Reflow mode extracts text and images from the original document, possibly "
"discarding some formatting, and reflows it on the screen for easier "
"reading.\n"
"Some of the other settings are only available when reflow mode is enabled."
msgstr ""
"Baintear téacs agus íomhánna as an doiciméad bunaidh sa mhodh athshreafa, "
"agus b'fhéidir go gcailltear cuid den fhormáidiú, agus athshreabhann sé ar "
"an scáileán é le go mbeidh sé níos fusa é a léamh.\n"
"Níl cuid de na socruithe eile ar fáil ach amháin nuair a bhíonn an modh "
"athshreafa cumasaithe."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:511
msgid "Dewatermark"
msgstr "Dí-uiscemharc"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:512
msgctxt "Dewatermark"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:512
msgctxt "Dewatermark"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:516
msgid ""
"Remove watermarks from the rendered document.\n"
"This can also be used to remove some gray background or to convert a "
"grayscale or color document to black & white and get more contrast for "
"easier reading."
msgstr ""
"Bain uiscemharcanna as an doiciméad rindreáilte.\n"
"Is féidir é seo a úsáid freisin chun roinnt cúlra liath a bhaint nó chun "
"doiciméad liathscála nó daite a thiontú go dubh agus bán agus codarsnacht "
"níos fearr a fháil le go mbeidh sé níos fusa é a léamh."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:521 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:534
msgid "Dithering"
msgstr "Díodán"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:522 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:535
msgctxt "Dithering"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:522 frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:535
msgctxt "Dithering"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:530
msgid "Enable hardware dithering."
msgstr "Cumasaigh díodán crua-earraí."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:543
msgid "Enable software dithering."
msgstr "Cumasaigh díodán bogearraí."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:547
msgctxt "Quality"
msgid "Render Quality"
msgstr "Cáilíocht Rindreála"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:548
msgctxt "Quality"
msgid "low"
msgstr "íseal"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:548
msgctxt "Quality"
msgid "default"
msgstr "réamhshocraithe"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:548
msgctxt "Quality"
msgid "high"
msgstr "ard"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:556
msgid ""
"In reflow mode, sets the quality of the text and image extraction processing "
"and output."
msgstr ""
"I mód athshreafa, socraítear cáilíocht phróiseáil agus aschur eastósctha "
"téacs agus íomhá."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:565
msgid "Document Language"
msgstr "Teanga an Doiciméid"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:575
msgid "Set the language to be used by the OCR engine."
msgstr "Socraigh an teanga atá le húsáid ag an inneall OCR."

#. @translators If OCR is unclear, please see https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Optical_character_recognition
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:580
msgid "Forced OCR"
msgstr "OCR Éigeantach"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:581
msgctxt "Forced OCR"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:581
msgctxt "Forced OCR"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:586
msgid ""
"Force the use of OCR for text selection, even if the document has a text "
"layer."
msgstr ""
"Éirigh úsáid OCR le haghaidh roghnú téacs, fiú má tá ciseal téacs sa "
"doiciméad."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:590
msgid "Writing Direction"
msgstr "Treo Scríbhneoireachta"

#. @translators LTR is left to right, which is the regular European writing direction.
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:596 frontend/ui/elements/page_turns.lua:152
msgid "LTR"
msgstr "LTR"

#. @translators RTL is right to left, which is the regular writing direction in languages like Hebrew, Arabic, Persian and Urdu.
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:598 frontend/ui/elements/page_turns.lua:159
msgid "RTL"
msgstr "RTL"

#. @translators TBRTL is top-to-bottom-right-to-left, which is a traditional Chinese/Japanese writing direction.
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:600
msgid "TBRTL"
msgstr "TBRTL"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:605
msgid ""
"In reflow mode, sets the original text direction. This needs to be set to "
"RTL to correctly extract and reflow RTL languages like Arabic or Hebrew."
msgstr ""
"I mód athshreafa, socraítear treo an téacs bhunaidh. Ní mór é seo a shocrú "
"go RTL chun teangacha RTL cosúil le Araibis nó Eabhrais a bhaint agus a "
"athshreabhadh i gceart."

#. @translators The maximum size of a dust or ink speckle to be ignored instead of being considered a character.
#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:610
msgid "Reflow Speckle Ignore Size"
msgstr "Méid Neamhaird a thabhairt ar Bhreac Athshreabhadh"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:611
msgctxt "Reflow speckle ignore size"
