msgstr "meánach"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:611
msgctxt "Reflow speckle ignore size"
msgid "large"
msgstr "mór"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:623
msgid "Indentation"
msgstr "Eangú"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:624
msgctxt "Indentation"
msgid "off"
msgstr "as"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:624
msgctxt "Indentation"
msgid "on"
msgstr "ar"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:635
msgid "Invert Document"
msgstr "Inbhéartaigh an Doiciméad"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:641
msgid ""
"Invert document in night mode. Useful for image-heavy documents such as "
"comics or manga."
msgstr ""
"Inbhéartaigh an doiciméad i mód oíche. Úsáideach do dhoiciméid ina bhfuil go "
"leor íomhánna ar nós greannáin nó manga."

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:645
msgid "Document Columns"
msgstr "Colúin Doiciméid"

#: frontend/ui/data/koptoptions.lua:657
msgid ""
"In reflow mode, sets the max number of columns to try to detect in the "
"original document.\n"
"You might need to set it to 1 column if, in a full width document, text is "
"incorrectly detected as multiple columns because of unlucky word spacing."
msgstr ""
"I mód athshreafa, socraítear an líon uasta colún le hiarracht a bhrath sa "
"doiciméad bunaidh.\n"
"B’fhéidir go mbeadh ort é a shocrú go 1 cholún má bhraitear téacs go "
"mícheart mar ilcholúin i ndoiciméad lánleithid mar gheall ar spásáil focal "
"mí-ádhúil."

#: frontend/ui/data/onetime_migration.lua:553
