#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:536
msgid ""
"This sets how often to rewrite to disk global settings and book metadata, "
"including your current position and any highlights and bookmarks made, when "
"you're reading a document.\n"
"\n"
"The normal behavior is to save those only when the document is closed, or "
"your device suspended, or when exiting KOReader.\n"
"\n"
"Setting it to some interval may help prevent losing new settings/sidecar "
"data after a software crash, but will cause more I/O writes the lower the "
"interval is, and may slowly wear out your storage media in the long run."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn sé seo cé chomh minic is ceart socruithe domhanda agus "
"meiteashonraí leabhar a athscríobh chuig diosca, lena n-áirítear do shuíomh "
"reatha agus aon bhuaicphointí agus leabharmharcanna a rinneadh, agus tú ag "
"léamh doiciméid.\n"
"\n"
"Is é an gnáthiompar ná iad sin a shábháil ach amháin nuair a bhíonn an "
"doiciméad dúnta, nó do ghléas ar fionraí, nó nuair a bhíonn tú ag fágáil "
"KOReader.\n"
"\n"
"D’fhéadfadh sé go gcuideodh sé le cosc a chur ar chailliúint socruithe nua/"
"sonraí taobhlíne tar éis tuairteála bogearraí, ach is cúis le níos mó "
"scríobhtaí I/O dá ísle an t-eatramh, agus d’fhéadfadh sé do mheán stórála a "
"chaitheamh go mall san fhadtréimhse."

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:547
msgid ""
"Please be warned that on this device, setting a low interval may exacerbate "
"the potential for filesystem corruption and complete data loss after a "
"hardware crash."
msgstr ""
"Tabhair faoi deara le do thoil, le do thoil, go bhféadfadh eatramh íseal a "
"shocrú ar an ngléas seo an baol a bhaineann le truailliú córas comhad agus "
"cailliúint iomlán sonraí a dhéanamh níos measa tar éis tuairteála crua-"
"earraí."

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:555
msgid "Only on close and suspend"
msgstr "Ar dhúnadh agus ar fionraí amháin"

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:557
msgid "Every minute"
msgid_plural "Every %1 minutes"
msgstr[0] "Gach nóiméad"
msgstr[1] "Gach %1 nóiméad"
msgstr[2] "Gach %1 nóiméad"
msgstr[3] "Gach %1 nóiméad"
msgstr[4] "Gach %1 nóiméad"

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:573
msgid "Document"
msgstr "Doiciméad"

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:578
msgid "book folder"
msgstr "fillteán leabhar"

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:584
msgid ""
"Book view settings, reading progress, highlights, bookmarks and notes "
"(collectively known as metadata) are stored in a separate folder named <book-"
"filename>.sdr (\".sdr\" meaning \"sidecar\")."
msgstr ""
"Stóráiltear socruithe radhairc leabhair, dul chun cinn léitheoireachta, "
"buaicphointí, leabharmharcanna agus nótaí (ar a dtugtar meiteashonraí le "
"chéile) i bhfillteán ar leith darb ainm <ainm comhaid-leabhair>.sdr "
"(\".sdr\" a chiallaíonn \"carr taobh\")."

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:586
msgid ""
"You can decide between three locations/methods where these will be saved:"
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat rogha a dhéanamh idir trí shuíomh/mhodh inar sábhálfar iad "
"seo:"

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:587
msgid ""
" - alongside the book file itself (the long time default): sdr folders will "
"be visible when you browse your library directories with another file "
"browser or from your computer, which may clutter your vision of your "
"library. But this allows you to move them along when you reorganize your "
"library, and also survives any renaming of parent directories. Also, if you "
"perform directory synchronization or backups, your settings will be part of "
"them."
msgstr ""
" - taobh leis an gcomhad leabhair féin (an réamhshocrú fadtréimhseach): "
"beidh fillteáin sdr le feiceáil nuair a bhrabhsálann tú eolairí do "
"leabharlainne le brabhsálaí comhad eile nó ó do ríomhaire, rud a d'fhéadfadh "
"cur isteach ar do radharc ar do leabharlann. Ach ligeann sé seo duit iad a "
"bhogadh ar aghaidh nuair a atheagraíonn tú do leabharlann, agus maireann sé "
"aon athainmniú ar eolairí tuismitheora freisin. Chomh maith leis sin, má "
"dhéanann tú sioncrónú eolaire nó cúltacaí, beidh do shocruithe mar chuid "
"díobh."

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:588
msgid ""
" - all in %1: sdr folders will only be visible and used by KOReader, and "
"won't clutter your vision of your library directories with another file "
"browser or from your computer. But any reorganisation of your library "
"(directories or filename moves and renamings) may result in KOReader not "
"finding your previous settings for these books. These settings won't be part "
"of any synchronization or backups of your library."
msgstr ""
" - gach rud i %1: ní bheidh fillteáin sdr le feiceáil agus in úsáid ach ag "
"KOReader, agus ní chuirfidh siad isteach ar do radharc ar eolairí do "
"leabharlainne le brabhsálaí comhad eile nó ó do ríomhaire. Ach d'fhéadfadh "
"sé nach bhfaighidh KOReader do shocruithe roimhe seo do na leabhair seo mar "
"thoradh ar aon atheagrú ar do leabharlann (bogadh agus athainmniú eolairí nó "
"ainmneacha comhad). Ní bheidh na socruithe seo mar chuid d'aon sioncrónú ná "
"cúltacaí de do leabharlann."

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:589
msgid ""
" - all inside %1 as hashes: sdr folders are identified not by filepath/"
"filename but by partial MD5 hash, allowing you to rename, move, and copy "
"documents outside of KOReader without sdr folder clutter while keeping them "
"linked to their metadata. However, any file modifications such as writing "
"highlights into PDFs or downloading from calibre may change the hash, and "
"thus lose their linked metadata. Calculating file hashes may also slow down "
"file browser navigation. This option may suit users with multiple copies of "
"documents across different devices and directories."
msgstr ""
" - gach ceann taobh istigh de %1 mar haiseanna: ní de réir cosáin/ainm "
"comhaid a shainaithnítear fillteáin sdr ach de réir hais MD5 pháirteach, rud "
"a ligeann duit doiciméid a athainmniú, a bhogadh agus a chóipeáil lasmuigh "
"de KOReader gan praiseach fillteán sdr agus iad a choinneáil nasctha lena "
"meiteashonraí. Mar sin féin, féadfaidh aon mhodhnuithe comhaid amhail "
"buaicphointí a scríobh i PDFanna nó iad a íoslódáil ó calibre an hais a "
"athrú, agus dá bhrí sin a meiteashonraí nasctha a chailleadh. Féadfaidh "
"ríomh haiseanna comhad moill a chur ar nascleanúint brabhsálaí comhad "
"freisin. D’fhéadfadh an rogha seo a bheith oiriúnach d’úsáideoirí a bhfuil "
"ilchóipeanna de dhoiciméid acu ar fud gléasanna agus eolairí éagsúla."

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:593
msgid ""
"%1 requires calculating partial file hashes of documents which may slow down "
"file browser navigation. Any file modifications (such as embedding "
"annotations into PDF files or downloading from calibre) may change the "
"partial hash, thereby losing track of any highlights, bookmarks, and "
"progress data. Embedding PDF annotations can be set at menu Typeset → "
"Highlights → Write highlights into PDF."
msgstr ""
"Éilíonn %1 ríomh haiseáin chomhaid pháirteacha de dhoiciméid a d'fhéadfadh "
"moill a chur ar nascleanúint an bhrabhsálaí comhad. Féadfaidh aon "
"mhodhnuithe comhaid (amhail anótálacha a leabú i gcomhaid PDF nó íoslódáil ó "
"calibre) an haiseán páirteach a athrú, rud a fhágann go gcaillfear rian ar "
"aon bhuaicphointí, leabharmharcanna, agus sonraí dul chun cinn. Is féidir "
"leabú anótálacha PDF a shocrú ag an roghchlár Clósocrú → Buaicphointí → "
"Scríobh buaicphointí i PDF."

#: frontend/ui/elements/common_settings_menu_table.lua:594
msgid ""
"Warning: You currently have documents with hash-based metadata. Until this "
"metadata is moved by opening those documents, or deleted, file browser "
"navigation may remain slower."
msgstr ""
"Rabhadh: Tá doiciméid agat faoi láthair a bhfuil meiteashonraí bunaithe ar "
