msgid "This will inhibit automatic rotations triggered by your device's gyro."
msgstr ""
"Cuirfidh sé seo cosc ar rothlaithe uathoibríocha a spreagann gyro do ghléis."

#: frontend/ui/elements/screen_rotation_menu_table.lua:47
msgid "Lock auto rotation to current orientation"
msgstr "Glasáil rothlú uathoibríoch go dtí an treoshuíomh reatha"

#: frontend/ui/elements/screen_rotation_menu_table.lua:48
msgid ""
"When checked, the gyro will only be honored when switching between the two "
"inverse variants of your current rotation,\n"
"i.e., Portrait <-> Inverted Portrait OR Landscape <-> Inverted Landscape.\n"
"Switching between (Inverted) Portrait and (Inverted) Landscape will be "
"inhibited.\n"
"If you need to do so, you'll have to use the UI toggles."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bheidh sé seo seiceáilte, ní ghlacfar leis an ngiro ach amháin nuair "
"a bheidh tú ag aistriú idir an dá chineál inbhéartaithe de do rothlú "
"reatha,\n"
"i.e., Portráid <-> Portráid Inbhéartaithe NÓ Tírdhreach <-> Tírdhreach "
"Inbhéartaithe.\n"
"Beidh cosc ar aistriú idir Portráid (Inbhéartaithe) agus Tírdhreach "
"(Inbhéartaithe).\n"
"Más gá duit é sin a dhéanamh, beidh ort na lasca comhéadain úsáideora a "
"úsáid."

#: frontend/ui/elements/screen_rotation_menu_table.lua:66
msgid "Keep current rotation across views"
msgstr "Coinnigh an rothlú reatha trasna na radharcanna"

#: frontend/ui/elements/screen_rotation_menu_table.lua:67
msgid ""
"When checked, the current rotation will be kept when switching between the "
"file browser and the reader, in both directions, and that no matter what the "
"document's saved rotation or the default reader or file browser rotation may "
"be.\n"
"This means that nothing will ever sneak a rotation behind your back, you "
"choose your device's rotation, and it stays that way.\n"
"When unchecked, the default rotation of the file browser and the default/"
"saved reader rotation will not affect each other (i.e., they will be "
"honored), and may very well be different."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn sé seo seiceáilte, coinneofar an rothlú reatha agus tú ag "
"aistriú idir an brabhsálaí comhad agus an léitheoir, sa dá threo, agus is "
"cuma cén rothlú sábháilte atá ar an doiciméad nó an léitheoir "
"réamhshocraithe nó rothlú an bhrabhsálaí comhad.\n"
"Ciallaíonn sé seo nach ndéanfaidh aon rud rothlú a cheilt taobh thiar de do "
"dhroim, roghnaíonn tú rothlú do ghléis, agus fanann sé mar sin.\n"
"Nuair nach mbíonn sé seiceáilte, ní bheidh tionchar ag rothlú "
"réamhshocraithe an bhrabhsálaí comhad agus rothlú an léitheora "
"réamhshocraithe/sábháilte ar a chéile (i.e., déanfar iad a urramú), agus "
"d'fhéadfadh siad a bheith difriúil go maith."

