#: frontend/ui/network/manager.lua:921
msgid ""
"This will automatically turn Wi-Fi off after a generous period of network "
"inactivity, without disrupting workflows that require a network connection, "
"so you can just keep reading without worrying about battery drain."
msgstr ""
"Múchfaidh sé seo Wi-Fi go huathoibríoch tar éis tréimhse fhaithiúil "
"neamhghníomhaíochta líonra, gan cur isteach ar shreabhadh oibre a bhfuil "
"nasc líonra ag teastáil uathu, ionas gur féidir leat leanúint ar aghaidh ag "
"léamh gan a bheith buartha faoi dhraenáil ceallraí."

