#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:115
msgid ""
"## User interface <a id=\"ui\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block\">![Touch zones](resources/quickstart/"
"touchzones.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- To show the **TOP MENU** or **BOTTOM MENU** you can click the indicated "
