"féidir leat cliceáil ar na criosanna léirithe. Is féidir leat cliceáil nó "
"svaidhpeáil síos an crios uachtarach chun an **ROGHCHLÁR BARR** a "
"thaispeáint.\n"
"- Is féidir an crios **BARRA STÁDAIS** a úsáid chun rothlú idir míreanna "
"BARRA STÁDAIS má tá mír amháin le feiceáil. Folóidh sé seo an BARRA STÁDAIS "
"agus taispeánfaidh sé é freisin má thapálann tú go leor uaireanta.\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:127
msgid ""
"## User interface tips <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- You can change the interface language using:\n"
"\n"
"> **Menu ➔ ![Settings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Language**\n"
"\n"
"- If you press both **ScreenKB** + **Press** on an option or menu item (font "
"weight, line spacing etc.), you can set its value as **DEFAULT**.  The new "
"value will only be applied to documents opened from now on. Previously "
"opened documents will keep their settings. You can identify default values "
"as a STAR in menu or as a black border around indicators as seen below:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 1](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 2](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- You can see explanations for some items on the **TOP MENU** by pressing "
"both **ScreenKB** + **Press** on the name of the option.\n"
"- You can **CLOSE** full screen dialogs (History, Table of Contents, "
"Bookmarks, Reading Statistics etc.) by pressing the **Back** key.\n"
"- **SCREENSHOTS** can be taken by pressing the **ScreenKB** + **Menu** keys\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Number picker](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- In dialogs containing adjustment arrow buttons like the one above, you can "
"use the directional keys to move around. If widgets have menus, pressing the "
"**Menu** key should open them.\n"
"- You can toggle content selection mode by pressing either the **Up** or "
"**Down** keys. The selection tool becomes available so you can select one or "
"multiple words, for either dictionary, wikipedia or text look ups.\n"
"- You can highlight blocks of text by selecting multiple words with the "
"content selection tool.\n"
"- You can move through your document with the **Left** or **Right** cursor "
"keys which, should take you to the previous or next chapter respectively.\n"
"- The content selection tool's sensitivity can be adjusted in the **TOP "
"MENU**.\n"
"\n"
"> **Menu ➔ ![Typesettings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) ➔ "
"Selection on text**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Leideanna maidir le comhéadan úsáideora <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- Is féidir leat teanga an chomhéadain a athrú trí úsáid a bhaint as:\n"
"\n"
"> **Roghchlár ➔ ![Socruithe](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Teanga**\n"
"\n"
"- Má bhrúnn tú **ScreenKB** + **Brúigh** ar rogha nó mír roghchláir (meáchan "
"cló, spásáil líne srl.), is féidir leat a luach a shocrú mar "
"**RÉAMHSHOCRAITHE**. Ní chuirfear an luach nua i bhfeidhm ach ar dhoiciméid "
"a osclaítear feasta. Coinneoidh doiciméid a osclaíodh roimhe seo a "
"socruithe. Is féidir leat luachanna réamhshocraithe a aithint mar RÉALTA sa "
"roghchlár nó mar imeall dubh timpeall ar tháscairí mar a fheictear thíos:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Socruithe réamhshocraithe 1]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Socruithe réamhshocraithe 2]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- Is féidir leat mínithe a fheiceáil ar roinnt míreanna ar an **BARR-"
"ROGHCHLÁR** trí bhrú ar **ScreenKB** + **Brúigh** ar ainm an rogha.\n"
"- Is féidir leat dialóga lánscáileáin (Stair, Clár Ábhair, Leabharmharcanna, "
"Staitisticí Léitheoireachta srl.) a **DHÚNADH** tríd an eochair **Ar Ais** a "
"bhrú.\n"
"- Is féidir **SCREENSCREEN** a thógáil trí na heochracha **ScreenKB** + "
"**Menu** a bhrú\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Number picker](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- I ndialóga ina bhfuil cnaipí saigheada coigeartaithe cosúil leis an gceann "
"thuas, is féidir leat na heochracha treorach a úsáid chun bogadh timpeall. "
"Má tá biachláir ag giuirléidí, ba chóir go n-osclófaí iad trí bhrú ar an "
"eochair **Roghchlár**.\n"
"- Is féidir leat mód roghnúcháin ábhair a athrú trí na heochracha **Suas** "
"nó **Síos** a bhrú. Bíonn an uirlis roghnúcháin ar fáil ionas gur féidir "
"leat focal amháin nó níos mó a roghnú, le haghaidh foclóir, Vicipéid nó "
"cuardaigh téacs.\n"
"- Is féidir leat bloic téacs a aibhsiú trí ilfhocail a roghnú leis an uirlis "
"roghnúcháin ábhair.\n"
"- Is féidir leat bogadh trí do dhoiciméad leis na heochracha cúrsóra **Clé** "
"nó **Deas**, agus ba chóir go dtabharfadh siad chuig an gcaibidil roimhe seo "
"nó an chéad chaibidil eile thú faoi seach.\n"
"- Is féidir íogaireacht na huirlise roghnúcháin ábhair a choigeartú sa "
"**BARR-ROGHCHLÁR**.\n"
"\n"
"> **Roghchlár ➔ ![SocruitheCló](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) "
"➔ Roghnú ar théacs**\n"

