"Language**\n"
"\n"
"- If you press both **Shift** + **Press** on an option or menu item (font "
"weight, line spacing etc.), you can set its value as **DEFAULT**.  The new "
"value will only be applied to documents opened from now on. Previously "
"opened documents will keep their settings. You can identify default values "
"as a STAR in menu or as a black border around indicators as seen below:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 1](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 2](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- You can see explanations for some items on the **TOP MENU** by pressing "
"both **Shift** + **Press** on the name of the option.\n"
"- You can **CLOSE** full screen dialogs (History, Table of Contents, "
"Bookmarks, Reading Statistics etc.) by pressing the **Back** key.\n"
"- **SCREENSHOTS** can be taken by pressing the **Alt** + **Shift** + **G** "
"keys\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Number picker](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- In dialogs containing adjustment arrow buttons like the one above, you can "
"use the directional keys to move around. If widgets have menus, pressing the "
"**Menu** key should open them.\n"
"- You can toggle content selection mode by pressing either the **Up** or "
"**Down** keys. The selection tool becomes available so you can select one or "
"multiple words, for either dictionary, wikipedia or text look ups.\n"
"- You can highlight blocks of text by selecting multiple words with the "
"content selection tool.\n"
"- You can move through your document with the **Left** or **Right** cursor "
"keys which, should take you to the previous or next chapter respectively.\n"
"- The content selection tool's sensitivity can be adjusted in the **TOP "
"MENU**.\n"
"\n"
"> **Menu ➔ ![Typesettings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) ➔ "
"Selection on text**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Leideanna maidir le comhéadan úsáideora <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- Is féidir leat teanga an chomhéadain a athrú trí úsáid a bhaint as:\n"
"\n"
"> **Roghchlár ➔ ![Socruithe](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Teanga**\n"
"\n"
"- Má bhrúnn tú **Shift** + **Brúigh** ar rogha nó ar mhír roghchláir "
"(meáchan cló, spásáil líne srl.), is féidir leat a luach a shocrú mar "
"**RÉAMHSHOCRAITHE**. Ní chuirfear an luach nua i bhfeidhm ach ar dhoiciméid "
"a osclaítear feasta. Coinneoidh doiciméid a osclaíodh roimhe seo a "
"socruithe. Is féidir leat luachanna réamhshocraithe a aithint mar RÉALTA sa "
"roghchlár nó mar imeall dubh timpeall ar tháscairí mar a fheictear thíos:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Socruithe réamhshocraithe 1]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Socruithe réamhshocraithe 2]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- Is féidir leat mínithe a fheiceáil ar roinnt míreanna ar an **ROGHCHLÁR "
"BARR** trí bhrú ar **Shift** + **Brúigh** ar ainm an rogha.\n"
"- Is féidir leat dialóga lánscáileáin (Stair, Clár Ábhair, Leabharmharcanna, "
"Staitisticí Léitheoireachta srl.) a **DHÚNADH** tríd an eochair **Ar Ais** a "
"bhrú.\n"
"- Is féidir **SCREENSCREEN** a thógáil trí na heochracha **Alt** + **Shift** "
"+ **G** a bhrú\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Number picker](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- I ndialóga ina bhfuil cnaipí saigheada coigeartaithe cosúil leis an gceann "
"thuas, is féidir leat na heochracha treorach a úsáid chun bogadh timpeall. "
"Má tá biachláir ag giuirléidí, ba chóir go n-osclófaí iad trí bhrú ar an "
"eochair **Roghchlár**.\n"
"- Is féidir leat mód roghnúcháin ábhair a athrú trí na heochracha **Suas** "
"nó **Síos** a bhrú. Bíonn an uirlis roghnúcháin ar fáil ionas gur féidir "
"leat focal amháin nó níos mó a roghnú, le haghaidh foclóir, Vicipéid nó "
"cuardaigh téacs.\n"
"- Is féidir leat bloic téacs a aibhsiú trí ilfhocail a roghnú leis an uirlis "
"roghnúcháin ábhair.\n"
"- Is féidir leat bogadh trí do dhoiciméad leis na heochracha cúrsóra **Clé** "
"nó **Deas**, agus ba chóir go dtabharfadh siad chuig an gcaibidil roimhe seo "
"nó an chéad chaibidil eile thú faoi seach.\n"
"- Is féidir íogaireacht na huirlise roghnúcháin ábhair a choigeartú sa "
"**BARR-ROGHCHLÁR**.\n"
"\n"
"> **Roghchlár ➔ ![SocruitheCló](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.typeset.svg) "
"➔ Roghnú ar théacs**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:181
msgid ""
"## User interface tips <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- You can change the interface language using:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU ➔ ![Settings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Language**\n"
"\n"
"- If you tap and hold on an option or menu item (font weight, line spacing "
"etc.), you can set its value as **DEFAULT**.  The new value will only be "
"applied to documents opened from now on. Previously opened documents will "
"keep their settings. You can identify default values as a STAR in menu or as "
"a black border around indicators as seen below:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 1](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Default setting 2](resources/"
"quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- You can see explanations for all items on the **BOTTOM MENU** by tapping "
"and holding the name of the option. This is also available for most of the "
"**TOP MENU** menu items.\n"
"- You can **CLOSE** full screen dialogs (History, Table of Contents, "
"Bookmarks, Reading Statistics etc.) by swiping down\n"
"- **SCREENSHOTS** can be taken by touching opposing corners of the screen "
"diagonally at the same time or by making a long diagonal swipe\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Number picker](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- In dialogs containing adjustment arrow buttons like the one above, you can "
"tap and hold on arrow buttons to increase / decrease the value in bigger "
"increments\n"
"- You can **CLOSE** this type of dialog (non-full screen) by tapping outside "
"of the window. You can **MOVE** this type of dialog by holding the window "
"title and dragging\n"
"- You can make this type of dialog **SEMI-TRANSPARENT** (to see the text "
"under it while adjusting a value) by tapping and holding the window title\n"
"- Tapping and holding a word brings up a dialog which allows you to search "
"for the selection to find more occurrences in the document or to look it up "
"on Wikipedia\n"
"- You can highlight sections by tapping and holding a word and dragging your "
"finger\n"
"- You can move through your document via the **SKIM DOCUMENT** dialog:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU ➔ ![Navigation](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.navigation.svg) "
"➔ Skim document**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Leideanna maidir le comhéadan úsáideora <a id=\"uitips\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"- Is féidir leat teanga an chomhéadain a athrú trí úsáid a bhaint as:\n"
"\n"
"> **BARR-ROGHCHLÁR ➔ ![Socruithe](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.settings.svg) ➔ Teanga**\n"
"\n"
"- Má thapaíonn tú agus má choinníonn tú síos rogha nó mír roghchláir "
"(meáchan cló, spásáil líne srl.), is féidir leat a luach a shocrú mar "
"**RÉAMHSHOCRAITHE**. Ní chuirfear an luach nua i bhfeidhm ach ar dhoiciméid "
"a osclaítear feasta. Coinneoidh doiciméid a osclaíodh roimhe seo a "
"socruithe. Is féidir leat luachanna réamhshocraithe a aithint mar RÉALTA sa "
"roghchlár nó mar imeall dubh timpeall ar tháscairí mar a fheictear thíos:\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Socruithe réamhshocraithe 1]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting1.png)</div>\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-before-avoid\">![Socruithe réamhshocraithe 2]"
"(resources/quickstart/defaultsetting2.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- Is féidir leat mínithe a fheiceáil do na míreanna go léir ar an "
"**ROGHCHLÁR BUN** trí ainm an rogha a thapáil agus a shealbhú. Tá sé seo ar "
"fáil freisin don chuid is mó de na míreanna roghchláir **ROGHCHLÁR BARR**. \n"
"- Is féidir leat dialóga lánscáileáin (Stair, Clár Ábhair, Leabharmharcanna, "
"Staitisticí Léitheoireachta srl.) a **DHÚNADH** trí shlaodadh síos\n"
"- Is féidir **GRIANGHTAÍ SCÁILEÁIN** a thógáil trí choirnéil urchomhaireacha "
"an scáileáin a theagmháil go trasnánach ag an am céanna nó trí shlaodadh "
"fada trasnánach a dhéanamh\n"
"\n"
"<div class=\"img-block break-after-avoid\">![Roghnóir uimhreacha](resources/"
"quickstart/numberpicker.png)</div>\n"
"\n"
"- I ndialóga ina bhfuil cnaipí saigheada coigeartaithe cosúil leis an gceann "
"thuas, is féidir leat na cnaipí saigheada a thapáil agus a shealbhú chun an "
"luach a mhéadú/laghdú i méaduithe níos mó\n"
"- Is féidir leat an cineál seo dialóige (nach lánscáileán) a **DHÚNADH** trí "
"thapáil lasmuigh den fhuinneog. Is féidir leat an cineál seo dialóige a "
"**BHOGADH** trí theideal na fuinneoige a shealbhú agus a tharraingt\n"
"- Is féidir leat an cineál seo dialóige a dhéanamh **LEATHTHRÉDHEARCACH** "
"(chun an téacs faoi a fheiceáil agus luach á choigeartú) trí theideal na "
"fuinneoige a thapáil agus a shealbhú\n"
"- Trí fhocal a thapáil agus a shealbhú, tugtar dialóg aníos a ligeann duit "
"an rogha a chuardach chun níos mó cásanna sa doiciméad a aimsiú nó chun é a "
"chuardach ar Vicipéid\n"
"- Is féidir leat ailt a aibhsiú trí fhocal a thapáil agus a shealbhú agus do "
"mhéar a tharraingt\n"
"- Is féidir leat bogadh trí do dhoiciméad tríd an dialóg **DOICIMÉAD "
"LÉIRMHEÁIL**:\n"
"\n"
"> **BARR-ROGHCHLÁR ➔ ![Nascleanúint](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.navigation.svg) ➔ Doiciméad léimneach**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:213
msgid ""
"## Accessing files <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following methods are available for accessing your books and articles:\n"
"\n"
"* File Browser\n"
"* Favorites\n"
"* History\n"
"\n"
"You can also set KOReader to open with any of these dialogs on startup via:\n"
"\n"
"> **Menu (in File Browser) ➔ ![Filebrowser](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Start with**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Rochtain ar chomhaid <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Tá na modhanna seo a leanas ar fáil chun rochtain a fháil ar do leabhair "
"agus d'ailt:\n"
"\n"
"* Brabhsálaí Comhad\n"
"* Ceanáin\n"
"* Stair\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat KOReader a shocrú chun oscailt le haon cheann de na dialóga "
"seo ag am tosaithe trí:\n"
"\n"
"> **Roghchlár (sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad) ➔ ![Brabhsálaí Comhad](resources/icons/"
"mdlight/appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Tosaigh le**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:227
msgid ""
"## Accessing files <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following methods are available for accessing your books and articles:\n"
"\n"
"* File Browser\n"
"* Favorites\n"
"* History\n"
"\n"
"You can assign gestures for quick access to each of these dialogs.\n"
"\n"
"You can also set KOReader to open with any of these dialogs on startup via:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU (in File Browser) ➔ ![Filebrowser](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Start with**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Rochtain ar chomhaid <a id=\"afiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Tá na modhanna seo a leanas ar fáil chun rochtain a fháil ar do leabhair "
"agus d'ailt:\n"
"\n"
"* Brabhsálaí Comhad\n"
"* Ceanáin\n"
"* Stair\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat gothaí a shannadh le haghaidh rochtain thapa ar gach ceann de "
"na dialóga seo.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat KOReader a shocrú freisin chun oscailt le haon cheann de na "
