"\n"
"> **BARR-ROGHCHLÁR (sa Bhrabhsálaí Comhad) ➔ ![Brabhsálaí Comhad](resources/"
"icons/mdlight/appbar.filebrowser.svg) ➔ Tosaigh le**\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:245
msgid ""
"## Transferring files <a id=\"tfiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"In addition to transferring files the same way you would with the built-in "
"reader application, other options are available depending on your device:\n"
"\n"
"1. USB Mass Storage mode within KOReader\n"
"2. Cloud storage (Dropbox/FTP/Webdav)\n"
"3. SSH/SFTP access\n"
"4. Calibre transfer\n"
"5. News downloader\n"
"6. Wallabag\n"
msgstr ""
"## Comhaid a aistriú <a id=\"tfiles\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Chomh maith le comhaid a aistriú ar an mbealach céanna a dhéanfá leis an "
"bhfeidhmchlár léitheoireachta ionsuite, tá roghanna eile ar fáil ag brath ar "
"do ghléas:\n"
"\n"
"1. Mód Stórála Mais USB laistigh de KOReader\n"
"2. Stóráil scamall (Dropbox/FTP/Webdav)\n"
"3. Rochtain SSH/SFTP\n"
"4. Aistriú Calibre\n"
"5. Íoslódálaí nuachta\n"
"6. Wallabag\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:260
msgid ""
"## Shortcuts <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following is a non-exhaustive list of shortcuts available.\n"
"\n"
"When inside the reading module:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Up**: Table of contents\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Right**: Add a bookmark\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Down**: Book map\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Left**: Bookmarks, notes and highlights\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Press**: Save current page to location history\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Home**: Toggle wifi on/off\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Back**: Switch to previously opened book\n"
"\n"
"When using a virtual keyboard:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Right**: Move cursor to right char\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Left**: Move cursor to left char\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Press**: Show special characters behind virtual keyboard "
"keys\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Home**: Toggle virtual keyboard on/off\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Back**: Delete char\n"
msgstr ""
"## Aicearraí <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Seo a leanas liosta neamh-uileghabhálach de na haicearraí atá ar fáil.\n"
"\n"
"Nuair atá tú istigh sa mhodúl léitheoireachta:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Suas**: Clár ábhair\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Deas**: Cuir leabharmharc leis\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Síos**: Léarscáil leabhar\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Clé**: Leabharmharcanna, nótaí agus buaicphointí\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Brúigh**: Sábháil an leathanach reatha chuig stair na "
"suíomhanna\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Baile**: Scoránaigh wifi ar siúl/as\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Ar Ais**: Athraigh go leabhar a osclaíodh roimhe seo\n"
"\n"
"Nuair a bhíonn méarchlár fíorúil in úsáid agat:\n"
"\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Deas**: Bog an cúrsóir go dtí an carachtar ar dheis\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Clé**: Bog an cúrsóir go dtí an carachtar ar chlé\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Brúigh**: Taispeáin carachtair speisialta taobh thiar de "
"na heochracha méarchláir fhíorúla\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Baile**: Scoránaigh an méarchlár fíorúil ar siúl/as\n"
"- **ScreenKB** + **Ar Ais**: Scrios an carachtar\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:284
msgid ""
"## Shortcuts <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"The following is a non-exhaustive list of shortcuts available.\n"
"\n"
"When inside the reading module:\n"
"\n"
"- **T** or **Shift** + **Up**: Table of contents\n"
"- **Shift** + **Right**: Add a bookmark\n"
"- **Shift** + **Down**: Book map\n"
"- **B** or **Shift** + **Left**: Bookmarks, notes and highlights\n"
"- **Shift** + **Press**: Save current page to location history\n"
"- **Shift** + **Home**: Toggle wifi on/off\n"
"- **Shift** + **Back**: Switch to previously opened book\n"
"\n"
"When using a virtual keyboard:\n"
"\n"
"- **Shift** + **Right**: Move cursor to right char\n"
"- **Shift** + **Left**: Move cursor to left char\n"
"- **Shift** + **Press**: Show special characters behind virtual keyboard "
"keys\n"
"- **Shift** + **Home**: Toggle virtual keyboard on/off\n"
"- **Shift** + **Del**: Delete word\n"
"- **Shift** + **Back**: Delete whole line\n"
"- **Sym** + **Alphabet keys**: symbols, numbers and special characters\n"
msgstr ""
"## Aicearraí <a id=\"short\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Seo a leanas liosta neamh-uileghabhálach de na haicearraí atá ar fáil.\n"
"\n"
"Nuair atá tú istigh sa mhodúl léitheoireachta:\n"
"\n"
"- **T** nó **Shift** + **Suas**: Clár ábhair\n"
"- **Shift** + **Deas**: Cuir leabharmharc leis\n"
"- **Shift** + **Síos**: Léarscáil leabhar\n"
"- **B** nó **Shift** + **Clé**: Leabharmharcanna, nótaí agus buaicphointí\n"
"- **Shift** + **Brúigh**: Sábháil an leathanach reatha chuig stair na "
"suíomhanna\n"
"- **Shift** + **Baile**: Scoránaigh wifi ar siúl/as\n"
"- **Shift** + **Ar Ais**: Athraigh go leabhar a osclaíodh roimhe seo\n"
"\n"
"Nuair a bhíonn méarchlár fíorúil in úsáid agat:\n"
"\n"
"- **Shift** + **Ar Ais**: Bog an cúrsóir go dtí an carachtar ar dheis\n"
"- **Shift** + **Clé**: Bog an cúrsóir go dtí an carachtar ar chlé\n"
"- **Shift** + **Brúigh**: Taispeáin carachtair speisialta taobh thiar de na "
"heochracha méarchláir fhíorúla\n"
"- **Shift** + **Baile**: Scoránaigh an méarchlár fíorúil ar siúl/as\n"
"- **Shift** + **Del**: Scrios focal\n"
"- **Shift** + **Ar Ais**: Scrios an líne iomlán\n"
"- **Sym** + **Eochracha aibítre**: siombailí, uimhreacha agus carachtair "
"speisialta\n"

#: frontend/ui/quickstart.lua:310
msgid ""
"## Frontlight/backlight <a id=\"flight\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"You can control your screen light via this menu. If you have warm lighting "
"(normal white LEDs+orange ones) you can control them separately from this "
"dialog:\n"
"\n"
"> **TOP MENU ➔ ![Settings](resources/icons/mdlight/appbar.settings.svg) ➔ "
"Frontlight**\n"
msgstr ""
"## Solas Tosaigh/Solas Cúil <a id=\"flight\"></a>\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leat solas do scáileáin a rialú tríd an roghchlár seo. Má tá "
"soilsiú te agat (soilse LED bán gnáth + cinn oráiste) is féidir leat iad a "
"rialú ar leithligh ón dialóg seo:\n"
"\n"
"> **BARR-ROGHCHLÁR ➔ ![Socruithe](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.settings.svg) ➔ Solas Tosaigh**\n"

