"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Déan an cló níos mó\n"
"\n"
"**ROGHCHLÁR BUN ➔ ![Textsize](resources/icons/mdlight/"
"appbar.textsize.svg)**\n"
"\n"
"</div><div>\n"
"\n"
"Déan an cló níos troime\n"
"\n"
"**ROGHCHLÁR BUN ➔ ![Codarsnacht](resources/icons/mdlight/"
