#: frontend/ui/translator.lua:373
msgid ""
"With books that specify their main language in their metadata (most EPUBs "
"and FB2s), enabling this option will make this language the source language. "
"Otherwise, auto-detection or the selected language will be used.\n"
"This is useful:\n"
"- For books in a foreign language, where consistent translation is needed "
"and words in other languages are rare.\n"
"- For books in familiar languages, to get definitions for words from the "
"translation service."
msgstr ""
"I gcás leabhar a shonraíonn a bpríomhtheanga ina meiteashonraí (an chuid is "
"mó de na EPUBanna agus na FB2anna), má chuireann tú an rogha seo ar siúl, "
"déanfar an teanga sin mar an teanga foinse. Seachas sin, úsáidfear "
"uathbhrath nó an teanga roghnaithe.\n"
"Tá sé seo úsáideach:\n"
"- I gcás leabhar i dteanga iasachta, áit a bhfuil gá le haistriúchán "
"comhsheasmhach agus ina bhfuil focail i dteangacha eile annamh.\n"
"- I gcás leabhar i dteangacha a bhfuil cur amach acu orthu, chun "
"sainmhínithe ar fhocail a fháil ón tseirbhís aistriúcháin."

#: frontend/ui/translator.lua:389
msgid "Auto-detect source language"
msgstr "Uath-bhrath a chur ar an teanga foinse"

#: frontend/ui/translator.lua:390
msgid ""
"This setting is best suited for foreign text found in books written in your "
"native language."
msgstr ""
"Is fearr a oireann an socrú seo do théacs coigríche atá le fáil i leabhair "
"atá scríofa i do theanga dhúchais."

#: frontend/ui/translator.lua:403
msgid "Show romanizations"
msgstr "Taispeáin na hainmneacha laidineacha"

#: frontend/ui/translator.lua:404
msgid ""
"Displays source language text in Latin characters. This is useful for "
"reading languages with non-Latin scripts."
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann sé téacs na teanga foinse i gcarachtair Laidine. Tá sé seo "
"úsáideach chun teangacha a léamh le scripteanna neamh-Laidine."

#: frontend/ui/translator.lua:415
msgid "Translate from: %1"
msgstr "Aistrigh ó: %1"

#: frontend/ui/translator.lua:417
msgid ""
"If a specific source language is manually selected, it will be used "
"everywhere, in all your books."
msgstr ""
"Má roghnaítear teanga foinse ar leith de láimh, úsáidfear í i ngach áit, i "
"do chuid leabhar go léir."

