#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1504
msgid ""
"Book map provides a summary of a book's content, showing chapters and pages "
"visually. If statistics are enabled, black bars represent pages already read "
"(gray for pages read in the current session), with varying heights based on "
"reading time.\n"
"\n"
"Map legend:\n"
"▲ current page\n"
"❶ ❷ … previous locations\n"
"① ② … next locations\n"
"▒ highlighted text\n"
" highlighted text with notes\n"
" bookmarked page\n"
" pinned page\n"
"▢ focused page when coming from Pages browser"
msgstr ""
"Tugann léarscáil leabhar achoimre ar ábhar leabhair, ag taispeáint caibidlí "
"agus leathanaigh go hamhairc. Má tá staitisticí cumasaithe, léiríonn barraí "
"dubha leathanaigh atá léite cheana féin (liath do leathanaigh atá léite sa "
"seisiún reatha), le hairde éagsúla bunaithe ar am léitheoireachta.\n"
"\n"
"Eochairléarscáil an léarscáil:\n"
"▲ leathanach reatha\n"
"❶ ❷ … suíomhanna roimhe seo\n"
"① ② … suíomhanna eile\n"
"▒ téacs aibhsithe\n"
" téacs aibhsithe le nótaí\n"
" leathanach leabharmharcáilte\n"
" leathanach bioráilte\n"
"▢ leathanach fócasaithe nuair a thagann tú ó bhrabhsálaí Leathanaigh"

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1518
msgid ""
"When in overview mode, the book map is always displayed in grid mode to fit "
"on one screen. The chapter levels can be easily adjusted for the most "
"convenient overview experience."
msgstr ""
"Nuair atá an modh forbhreathnaithe i bhfeidhm, taispeántar léarscáil an "
"leabhair i mód eangaí i gcónaí le go n-oirfidh sé ar aon scáileán amháin. Is "
"féidir leibhéil na gcaibidlí a choigeartú go héasca chun an taithí "
"forbhreathnaithe is áisiúla a fháil."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1521
msgid ""
"When you first open a book, the book map will begin in grid mode, displaying "
"all chapter levels on one screen for a comprehensive overview of the book's "
"content."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a osclaíonn tú leabhar den chéad uair, tosóidh léarscáil an leabhair i "
"mód eangaí, ag taispeáint gach leibhéal caibidle ar scáileán amháin le "
"haghaidh forbhreathnú cuimsitheach ar ábhar an leabhair."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1530
msgid ""
"Use settings in this menu to change the level of chapters to include in the "
"book map, the view type (grid or flat) and the width of page slots.\n"
"\n"
"Use \"ScreenKB/Shift\" + \"Up/Down\" to scroll or use the page turn buttons "
"to move at a faster rate.\n"
"\n"
"Press back to exit the book map."
msgstr ""
"Úsáid na socruithe sa roghchlár seo chun leibhéal na gcaibidlí atá le cur "
"san áireamh sa léarscáil leabhar, an cineál radhairc (eangach nó cothrom) "
"agus leithead na sliotán leathanaigh a athrú.\n"
"\n"
"Úsáid \"ScreenKB/Shift\" + \"Suas/Síos\" chun scrollú nó úsáid na cnaipí "
"casadh leathanaigh chun bogadh ar ráta níos tapúla.\n"
"\n"
"Brúigh ar ais chun imeacht as léarscáil an leabhair."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1537
msgid ""
"Tap on a location in the book to browse thumbnails of the pages there.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe along the left screen edge to change the level of chapters to include "
"in the book map.\n"
"\n"
"Any multiswipe will close the book map."
msgstr ""
"Beartaigh ar shuíomh sa leabhar chun mionsamhlacha de na leathanaigh ann a "
"bhrabhsáil.\n"
"\n"
"Svaip feadh imeall clé an scáileáin chun leibhéal na gcaibidlí atá le cur "
"san áireamh sa léarscáil leabhair a athrú.\n"
"\n"
"Dúnfaidh aon il-shvaip an léarscáil leabhair."

#: frontend/ui/widget/bookmapwidget.lua:1544
msgid ""
"Tap on a location in the book to browse thumbnails of the pages there.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe along the left screen edge to change the level of chapters to include "
"in the book map, and the type of book map (grid or flat) when crossing the "
"level 0.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe along the bottom screen edge to change the width of page slots.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe or pan vertically on content to scroll.\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on ≡ to switch between current and initial views.\n"
"\n"
"Any multiswipe will close the book map."
msgstr ""
"Beartaigh ar shuíomh sa leabhar chun mionsamhlacha de na leathanaigh ann a "
"bhrabhsáil.\n"
"\n"
"Svaip feadh imeall clé an scáileáin chun leibhéal na gcaibidlí atá le cur "
"san áireamh sa léarscáil leabhair a athrú, agus cineál léarscáil an leabhair "
"(eangach nó cothrom) agus tú ag trasnú leibhéal 0.\n"
"\n"
"Svaip feadh imeall bun an scáileáin chun leithead na sliotán leathanaigh a "
"athrú.\n"
"\n"
"Svaip nó panáil go hingearach ar an ábhar chun scrollú.\n"
"\n"
"Brúigh fada ar ≡ chun aistriú idir an radharc reatha agus an radharc "
"tosaigh.\n"
"\n"
"Dúnfaidh aon il-svaip an léarscáil leabhair."

