#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1147
msgid ""
"Page browser shows thumbnails of a book's pages.\n"
"\n"
"The bottom ribbon displays an extract of the book map around the pages "
"displayed:\n"
"\n"
"If statistics are enabled, black bars indicate pages that have already been "
"read (gray bars for pages read in the current session). The height of these "
"bars varies based on the time spent reading each page.\n"
"Chapters are indicated above the pages they cover.\n"
"Below the pages, the following indicators may appear:\n"
"▲ current page\n"
"❶ ❷ … previous locations\n"
"① ② … next locations\n"
"▒ highlighted text\n"
" highlighted text with notes\n"
" bookmarked page\n"
" pinned page"
msgstr ""
"Taispeánann brabhsálaí leathanaigh mionsamhlacha de leathanaigh leabhair.\n"
"\n"
"Taispeánann an ribín bun sliocht den léarscáil leabhar timpeall na "
"leathanach a thaispeántar:\n"
"\n"
"Má tá staitisticí cumasaithe, léiríonn barraí dubha leathanaigh atá léite "
"cheana féin (barraí liatha do leathanaigh a léadh sa seisiún reatha). "
"Athraíonn airde na mbarraí seo bunaithe ar an am a chaitear ag léamh gach "
"leathanaigh.\n"
"Léirítear caibidlí os cionn na leathanach a chlúdaíonn siad.\n"
"Faoi bhun na leathanaigh, féadfaidh na táscairí seo a leanas a bheith le "
"feiceáil:\n"
"▲ leathanach reatha\n"
"❶ ❷ … suíomhanna roimhe seo\n"
"① ② … suíomhanna eile\n"
"▒ téacs aibhsithe\n"
" téacs aibhsithe le nótaí\n"
" leathanach leabharmharcáilte\n"
" leathanach bioráilte"

#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1168
msgid ""
"Swipe along the top or left screen edge to change the number of columns or "
"rows of thumbnails.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe vertically to move one row, horizontally to move one screen.\n"
"\n"
"Swipe horizontally in the bottom ribbon to move by the full stripe.\n"
"\n"
"Tap in the bottom ribbon on a page to focus thumbnails on this page.\n"
"\n"
"Tap on a thumbnail to read that page.\n"
"\n"
"Long-press on ≡ to decrease or reset the number of chapter levels shown in "
"the bottom ribbon.\n"
"\n"
"Any multiswipe will close the page browser."
msgstr ""
"Svaidhpeáil feadh imeall uachtarach nó clé an scáileáin chun líon na gcolún "
"nó na sraitheanna mionsamhlacha a athrú.\n"
"\n"
"Svaidhpeáil go hingearach chun sraith amháin a bhogadh, go cothrománach chun "
"scáileán amháin a bhogadh.\n"
"\n"
"Svaidhpeáil go cothrománach sa ribín bun chun bogadh leis an stríoc iomlán.\n"
"\n"
"Tapáil sa ribín bun ar leathanach chun mionsamhlacha a dhíriú ar an "
"leathanach seo.\n"
"\n"
"Tapáil ar mhionsamhail chun an leathanach sin a léamh.\n"
"\n"
"Brúigh fada ar ≡ chun líon na leibhéal caibidle a thaispeántar sa ribín bun "
"a laghdú nó a athshocrú.\n"
"\n"
"Dúnfaidh aon ilshvaidhpeáil an brabhsálaí leathanaigh."

#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1184
#: frontend/ui/widget/pagebrowserwidget.lua:1194
msgid ""
"The settings (in this menu) can be used to change the number of rows and "
"columns, whether to display page numbers, and to display different chapter-"
"levels in the bottom ribbon."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir na socruithe (sa roghchlár seo) a úsáid chun líon na sraitheanna "
"agus na gcolún a athrú, cibé acu ar cheart uimhreacha leathanach a "
"thaispeáint, agus chun leibhéil chaibidle éagsúla a thaispeáint sa ribín bun."

