#: plugins/autowarmth.koplugin/main.lua:581
msgid ""
"Set the frontlight warmth (if available) and night mode based on a time "
"schedule or the sun's position.\n"
"\n"
"There are three types of twilight:\n"
"\n"
"• Civil: You can read a newspaper\n"
"• Nautical: You can see the first stars\n"
"• Astronomical: It is really dark\n"
"\n"
"Custom warmth values can be set for every kind of twilight and sunrise, "
"noon, sunset and midnight.\n"
"The screen warmth is continuously adjusted to the current time.\n"
"\n"
"To use the sun's position, a geographical location must be entered. The "
"calculations are very precise, with a deviation less than minute and a half."
msgstr ""
"Socraigh teas an tsolais tosaigh (más féidir) agus mód na hoíche bunaithe ar "
"sceideal ama nó ar shuíomh na gréine.\n"
"\n"
"Tá trí chineál breacadh an lae ann:\n"
"\n"
"• Sibhialta: Is féidir leat nuachtán a léamh\n"
"• Loingseoireacht: Is féidir leat na chéad réaltaí a fheiceáil\n"
"• Réalteolaíoch: Tá sé an-dorcha\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir luachanna teasa saincheaptha a shocrú do gach cineál breacadh an "
"lae agus éirí gréine, meán lae, luí na gréine agus meán oíche.\n"
"Déantar teas an scáileáin a choigeartú go leanúnach go dtí an t-am reatha.\n"
"\n"
"Chun suíomh na gréine a úsáid, ní mór suíomh geografach a iontráil. Tá na "
"ríomhanna an-chruinn, le diall níos lú ná nóiméad go leith."

