#: plugins/coverimage.koplugin/main.lua:472
msgid ""
"This plugin saves a book cover to a file. That file can then be used as a "
"screensaver on certain devices.\n"
"\n"
"If enabled, the cover image of the current file is stored in the set path on "
"book opening. Books can be excluded if desired.\n"
"\n"
"If disabled, the cover file will be deleted.\n"
"\n"
"If fallback is enabled, the fallback file will be copied to the screensaver "
"file on book closing.\n"
"If the filename is empty or the file doesn't exist, the cover file will be "
"deleted.\n"
"\n"
"If fallback is disabled, the screensaver image will stay in place after "
"closing a book."
msgstr ""
"Sábhálann an breiseán seo clúdach leabhair chuig comhad. Is féidir an comhad "
"sin a úsáid ansin mar spárálaíscáileáin ar ghléasanna áirithe.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé cumasaithe, stóráiltear íomhá chlúdaigh an chomhaid reatha sa "
"chonair shocraithe nuair a osclaítear an leabhar. Is féidir leabhair a "
"eisiamh más mian leat.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá sé díchumasaithe, scriosfar an comhad clúdaigh.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá an rogha cúltaca cumasaithe, cóipeálfar an comhad cúltaca chuig an "
"gcomhad spárálaíscáileáin nuair a dhúnfar an leabhar.\n"
"Mura bhfuil ainm an chomhaid folamh nó mura bhfuil an comhad ann, scriosfar "
"an comhad clúdaigh.\n"
"\n"
"Má tá an rogha cúltaca díchumasaithe, fanfaidh íomhá an spárálaíscáileáin "
"ina háit tar éis leabhar a dhúnadh."

