#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:664
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:670
msgid "Text selection rate"
msgstr "Ráta roghnúcháin téacs"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:671
msgid ""
"The rate is how often screen will be refreshed per second while selecting "
"text.\n"
"Higher values mean faster screen updates, but also use more CPU."
msgstr ""
"Is é an ráta cé chomh minic a athnuachanfar an scáileán in aghaidh an "
"tsoicind agus téacs á roghnú.\n"
"Ciallaíonn luachanna níos airde nuashonruithe scáileáin níos tapúla, ach "
"úsáideann siad níos mó LAP freisin."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:680
msgctxt "Frequency"
msgid "Hz"
msgstr "Hz"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:681
msgid "Set rate"
msgstr "Socraigh an ráta"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:693
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:697
msgid "Tap interval"
msgstr "Eatramh sconna"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:698
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:725
msgid ""
"Any other taps made within this interval after a first tap will be "
"considered accidental and ignored.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 0 (0 seconds) to "
"2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Aon chnaganna eile a dhéantar laistigh den eatramh seo tar éis an chéad "
"chnag, measfar gur de thaisme a dhéantar iad agus ní dhéanfar aon neamhaird "
"orthu.\n"
"\n"
"Is i milleasoicindí a bhíonn an luach eatraimh agus féadann sé a bheith idir "
"0 (0 soicind) agus 2000 (2 shoicind)."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:720
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:724
msgid "Tap interval on keyboard"
msgstr "Eatramh tapála ar an méarchlár"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:746
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:750
msgid "Double tap interval"
msgstr "Eatramh sconna dúbailte"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:751
msgid ""
"When double tap is enabled, this sets the time to wait for the second tap. A "
"single tap will take at least this long to be detected.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) "
"to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Nuair a bhíonn tapáil dhúbailte cumasaithe, socraíonn sé seo an t-am a "
"chaithfear fanacht leis an dara tapáil. Tógfaidh sé seo an t-am seo ar a "
"laghad le tapáil aonair a bhrath.\n"
"\n"
"Is i milleasoicindí a bhíonn an luach eatraimh agus féadann sé a bheith idir "
"100 (0.1 soicind) agus 2000 (2 shoicind)."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:773
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:777
msgid "Two finger tap duration"
msgstr "Fad sconna dhá mhéar"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:778
msgid ""
"This sets the allowed duration of any of the two fingers touch/release for "
"the combined event to be considered a two finger tap.\n"
"\n"
"The duration value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) "
"to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn sé seo an fad ama a cheadaítear le haghaidh aon cheann de na dhá "
"mhéar a theagmháil/a scaoileadh le go measfar an teagmhas comhcheangailte "
"mar thapáil dhá mhéar.\n"
"\n"
"Is i milleasoicindí a bhíonn an luach fad ama agus féadann sé a bheith idir "
"100 (0.1 soicind) agus 2000 (2 shoicind)."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:789
msgid "Set duration"
msgstr "Socraigh fad"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:800
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:804
msgid "Long-press interval"
msgstr "Eatramh brú fada"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:805
msgid ""
"If a touch is not released in this interval, it is considered a long-press. "
"On document text, single word selection will then be triggered.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) "
"to the very-long-press interval."
msgstr ""
"Mura scaoiltear teagmháil laistigh den eatramh seo, meastar gur brú fada é. "
"Ar théacs an doiciméid, cuirfear tús le roghnú focal aonair ansin.\n"
"\n"
"Is i milleasoicindí a bhíonn an luach eatraimh agus féadann sé a bheith idir "
"100 (0.1 soicind) agus an t-eatramh brú an-fhada."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:828
#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:832
msgid "Swipe interval"
msgstr "Eatramh svaidhpeála"

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:833
msgid ""
"This sets the maximum delay between the start and the end of a swipe for it "
"to be considered a swipe. Above this interval, it's considered panning.\n"
"\n"
"The interval value is in milliseconds and can range from 100 (0.1 seconds) "
"to 2000 (2 seconds)."
msgstr ""
"Socraíonn sé seo an mhoill uasta idir tús agus deireadh svaidhpeála le go "
"measfar gur svaidhpeáil í. Os cionn an eatraimh seo, meastar gur panáil í.\n"
"\n"
"Tá luach an eatraimh i milleasoicindí agus féadann sé a bheith idir 100 (0.1 "
"soicind) agus 2000 (2 shoicind)."

#: plugins/gestures.koplugin/main.lua:860
