#: plugins/keepalive.koplugin/_meta.lua:4 plugins/keepalive.koplugin/main.lua:9
msgid "Keep alive"
msgstr "Coinnigh beo"

#: plugins/keepalive.koplugin/_meta.lua:5
msgid "Keeps the device awake to prevent automatic Wi-Fi disconnects."
msgstr ""
"Coinníonn sé an gléas ina dhúiseacht chun dícheangail uathoibríocha Wi-Fi a "
"chosc."

#: plugins/keepalive.koplugin/main.lua:18
msgid ""
"The system won't sleep while this message is showing.\n"
"\n"
"Press \"Stay alive\" if you prefer to keep the system on even after closing "
"this notification. *This will drain the battery*.\n"
"\n"
"If KOReader terminates before \"Close\" is pressed, please start and close "
"the KeepAlive plugin again to ensure settings are reset."
msgstr ""
"Ní rachaidh an córas i gcodladh agus an teachtaireacht seo á taispeáint.\n"
"\n"
"Brúigh \"Fan beo\" más fearr leat an córas a choinneáil ar siúl fiú tar éis "
"an fógra seo a dhúnadh. *Draenálfaidh sé seo an ceallraí*.\n"
"\n"
"Má chríochnaíonn KOReader sula mbrúitear \"Dún\", tosaigh agus dún an "
"breiseán KeepAlive arís le cinntiú go bhfuil na socruithe athshocraithe."

#: plugins/keepalive.koplugin/main.lua:25
msgid "Stay alive"
msgstr "Fan beo"

