"\n"
"There are two environment variables TERMINAL_HOME and TERMINAL_DATA "
"containing the path of the install and the data folders.\n"
"\n"
"Commands to be executed on start can be placed in:\n"
"'$TERMINAL_DATA/scripts/profile.user'.\n"
"\n"
"Aliases (shortcuts) to frequently used commands can be placed in:\n"
"'$TERMINAL_DATA/scripts/aliases'."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir le haithriseoir críochfoirt blaosc (pras ordaithe) a thosú.\n"
"\n"
"Tá dhá athróg timpeallachta ann, TERMINAL_HOME agus TERMINAL_DATA, ina "
"bhfuil cosán an suiteála agus na fillteáin sonraí.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir orduithe atá le cur i gcrích ag an tús a chur i:\n"
"'$TERMINAL_DATA/scripts/profile.user'.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir leasainmneacha (aicearraí) chuig orduithe a úsáidtear go minic a "
"chur i:\n"
"'$TERMINAL_DATA/scripts/aliases'."

