#: plugins/wallabag.koplugin/main.lua:513
msgid ""
"Download folder: use a folder that is exclusively used by the Wallabag "
"plugin. Existing files in this folder risk being deleted.\n"
"\n"
"Articles marked as finished, on hold or 100% read can be marked as read (or "
"deleted) on the server. This is done automatically when retrieving new "
"articles with the 'Auto-upload article statuses when downloading' setting.\n"
"\n"
"The 'Delete remotely archived and deleted articles locally' option will "
"allow deletion of local files that are archived or deleted on the server."
msgstr ""
"Fillteán íoslódála: bain úsáid as fillteán atá in úsáid go heisiach ag "
"breiseán Wallabag. Tá baol ann go scriosfar comhaid atá ann cheana féin sa "
"bhfillteán seo.\n"
"\n"
"Is féidir ailt atá marcáilte mar chríochnaithe, ar feitheamh nó 100% léite a "
"mharcáil mar léite (nó scriosta) ar an bhfreastalaí. Déantar é seo go "
"huathoibríoch agus ailt nua á n-aisghabháil leis an socrú 'Stádas ailt uath-"
"uaslódáilte agus á íoslódáil'.\n"
"\n"
"Ceadaíonn an rogha 'Scrios ailt atá cartlannaithe go cianda agus scriosta go "
"háitiúil' comhaid áitiúla atá cartlannaithe nó scriosta ar an bhfreastalaí a "
"scriosadh."

