#: tools/update-metadata.lua:26
msgid "Ebook reader"
msgstr "Léitheoir ríomhleabhar"

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:29
msgid ""
"KOReader is an ebook reader optimized for e-ink screens. It can open many "
"formats and provides advanced text adjustments."
msgstr ""
"Is léitheoir ríomhleabhar é KOReader atá optamaithe do scáileáin dúigh "
"leictreonacha. Is féidir leis go leor formáidí a oscailt agus cuireann sé "
"coigeartuithe téacs chun cinn ar fáil."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:30
msgid "See below for a selection of its many features:"
msgstr "Féach thíos le haghaidh rogha dá ghnéithe iomadúla:"

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:33
msgid ""
"Supports both fixed page formats (PDF, DjVu, CBT, CBZ) and reflowable e-book "
"formats (EPUB, FB2, Mobi, DOC, CHM, TXT, HTML). Scanned PDF/DjVu documents "
"can be reflowed. Special flow directions for reading double column PDFs and "
"manga."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíonn sé le formáidí leathanaigh sheasta (PDF, DjVu, CBT, CBZ) agus "
"formáidí ríomhleabhar in-athshreabhta (EPUB, FB2, Mobi, DOC, CHM, TXT, HTML) "
"araon. Is féidir doiciméid PDF/DjVu scanta a athshreabhadh. Treoracha sreafa "
"speisialta chun PDFanna dé-cholún agus manga a léamh."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:34
msgid ""
"Multi-lingual user interface optimized for e-ink screens. Highly "
"customizable reader view with complete typesetting options. Multi-lingual "
"hyphenation dictionaries are bundled in."
msgstr ""
"Comhéadan úsáideora ilteangach atá optamaithe do scáileáin dúigh "
"leictreonacha. Radharc léitheoirí atá an-shaincheaptha le roghanna "
"clóscríbhneoireachta iomlána. Tá foclóirí ilteangacha le haghaidh fleiscíní "
"pacáilte isteach."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:35
msgid ""
"Non-Latin script support for books, including the Hebrew, Arabic, Persian, "
"Russian, Chinese, Japanese and Korean languages."
msgstr ""
"Tacaíocht do scripteanna neamh-Laidineacha do leabhair, lena n-áirítear na "
"teangacha Eabhraise, Araibis, Peirsis, Rúisis, Sínis, Seapáinis agus "
"Cóiréise."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:36
msgid "Unique Book Map and Page Browser features to navigate your book."
msgstr ""
"Gnéithe uathúla Léarscáil Leabhar agus Brabhsálaí Leathanaigh chun "
"nascleanúint a dhéanamh i do leabhar."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:37
msgid ""
"Special multi-page highlight mode with many local and online export options."
msgstr ""
"Mód speisialta aibhsithe il-leathanaigh le go leor roghanna easpórtála "
"áitiúla agus ar líne."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:38
msgid ""
"Can synchronize your reading progress across all your KOReader running "
"devices."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat do dhul chun cinn léitheoireachta a shioncrónú ar fud do "
"ghléasanna uile atá ag rith KOReader."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:39
msgid ""
"Integrated with Calibre, Wallabag, Wikipedia, Google Translate and other "
"content providers."
msgstr ""
"Comhtháite le Calibre, Wallabag, Vicipéid, Google Translate agus "
"soláthraithe ábhair eile."

#: tools/update-metadata.lua:43
msgid "Release notes available on the link below"
msgstr "Nótaí scaoilte ar fáil ar an nasc thíos"

